Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:18.00,remark,,0000,0000,0000,,*《魔戒》的作者托尔金在书中创造了很多语言. 影片的语言标识如下：\N辛达语:斜体; 昆雅语:楷体; 矮人语:[ ]; 安度奈克语:/ /; 罗翰语:下划线
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.00,0:00:41.24,one_ring,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}《魔戒》
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.46,0:01:18.96,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,斯米戈尔!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.19,0:01:20.92,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我钓到一条!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.87,0:01:24.33,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我钓到一条鱼了, 斯米戈尔!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.36,0:01:27.44,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,快拉上来, 快点快点, 快拉上来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.58,0:01:37.21,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,迪戈尔!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.78,0:02:39.15,quenya ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪此为力量, 此为武器{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.60,0:02:36.43,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,迪戈尔?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.24,0:02:40.65,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,迪戈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.65,0:02:48.46,quenya ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪若需英勇, 可寻此戒{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.58,0:03:00.45,quenya ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}♪此为力量, 此为武器, 若得用之, 必获胜利!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.16,0:02:59.92,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,给我们吧, 迪戈尔, 亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.29,0:03:05.91,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.67,0:03:08.71,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,因为...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.82,0:03:12.81,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我过生日, 我想要它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.02,0:04:51.94,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我的宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:02.53,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他们诅咒我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:04.41,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,杀人犯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.44,0:05:06.70,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他们叫我们杀人犯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.76,0:05:11.40,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他们诅咒我们, 赶我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.99,0:05:14.54,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,咕噜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.84,0:05:16.26,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,咕噜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.63,0:05:18.19,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,咕噜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.27,0:05:25.24,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们哭了, 宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.29,0:05:28.91,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们孤单得哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.28,0:05:35.84,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,清又凉, 脚舒畅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.90,0:05:41.07,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,咱就只想抓条鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:44.48,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,味道甜又美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:53.99,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,于是我们忘记了面包的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.02,0:05:57.52,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,林木的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:06:01.95,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,微风的轻软
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.48,0:06:07.94,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们甚至忘记了自己的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.29,0:06:23.13,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我的宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.02,0:07:08.99,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.25,0:07:11.98,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.04,0:07:13.98,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,快醒醒, 瞌睡虫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.01,0:07:16.07,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得走了, 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:18.77,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得马上走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.38,0:07:25.00,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你难道没睡觉吗, 弗罗多先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.39,0:07:29.93,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经睡得太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.58,0:07:33.49,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,天色一定已经晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.52,0:07:34.98,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:36.95,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,还没呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.36,0:07:39.63,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,现在还没到中午
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.36,0:07:42.77,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,是天越来越黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:49.25,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,快点!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.02,0:07:54.37,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,快走! 没时间了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.40,0:07:56.75,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,得让弗罗多先生吃点东西再走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:07:59.50,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,没时间浪费了, 傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:10.12,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.11,0:08:14.73,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,那你呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:16.84,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 不用, 我还不饿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.87,0:08:18.74,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,至少不想吃兰巴斯面包
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.99,0:08:20.31,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,山姆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.01,0:08:24.45,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.75,0:08:26.89,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们剩的已经不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:30.15,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得小心安排, 不然就没得吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.39,0:08:34.97,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你先吃掉那块, 弗罗多先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.35,0:08:37.00,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经分配好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.32,0:08:39.05,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,应该够的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.43,0:08:42.84,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,够什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.19,0:08:45.85,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,回家路上吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.65,0:08:55.85,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,霍比特人快来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.47,0:08:59.44,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,现在非常近了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.45,0:09:02.70,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,离魔多非常近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.82,0:09:05.54,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这里不安全
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.67,0:09:07.75,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.37,0:09:56.16,one_ring,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\fad(300,300)\c&H746D3B&}《王者归来》
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.26,0:10:01.97,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.89,0:10:04.63,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,绝对是夏尔产的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.85,0:10:08.98,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,长底烟叶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:18.65,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得好像回到了绿龙酒馆似的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.63,0:10:20.81,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,绿龙酒馆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.81,0:10:23.16,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,手里端着一杯麦酒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.16,0:10:28.12,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦一整天以后把脚翘在长椅上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.50,0:10:32.12,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不过你还从来没有辛苦过一整天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:47.64,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,各位大人, 欢迎...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.81,0:10:49.95,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,来到伊森加德!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.33,0:10:52.50,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个小混蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:56.41,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,让我们追了一大圈, 你们却忙着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.67,0:10:59.58,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,大吃大喝...还抽上了烟!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.64,0:11:02.70,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们这可是坐在一堆胜利果实上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.78,0:11:06.07,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,享受应得的奖赏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.46,0:11:11.29,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这块腌猪肉尤其美味
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.92,0:11:13.95,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,腌猪肉?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:16.24,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,霍比特人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.24,0:11:19.01,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们听从树胡子的吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.17,0:11:22.38,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他已经接管伊森加德了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.23,0:11:27.58,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,年轻的甘道夫阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.61,0:11:32.14,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴你来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.22,0:11:36.73,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我能控制林木和水流、树干和岩石
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.80,0:11:40.57,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,但这里还有一位巫师不受管辖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.68,0:11:43.06,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,关在自个儿的高塔里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.20,0:11:46.85,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,现身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.88,0:11:48.64,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.37,0:11:52.28,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,即便落败了, 萨茹曼也很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.33,0:11:54.46,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,那就砍了他的脑袋, 就此了结
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.51,0:11:56.28,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.95,0:11:59.01,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要他活着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:02.59,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要他开口
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.53,0:12:08.52,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,塞奥顿王, 你经历了许多战争, 杀过许多人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.58,0:12:10.68,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,随后得到了和平
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.76,0:12:15.81,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能像以往那样一同商议吗, 我的老朋友?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.87,0:12:19.18,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你我之间就不能和平相处吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:21.63,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以和平相处
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.12,0:12:25.32,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以和平相处...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:29.54,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,只要你为焚毁西谷做个交代
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:32.99,remark,,0000,0000,0000,,*西谷位于罗翰西部, 临近伊森河, 萨茹曼的大军\N从西谷开始入侵罗翰, 逼迫塞奥顿王退守海尔姆深谷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.62,0:12:32.99,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,为那里死去的孩子做个交代!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:37.37,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以和平相处, 只要战士们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.43,0:12:41.63,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,在号角堡门前战死后尸身仍受凌辱的大仇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.66,0:12:44.01,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,终得报偿!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.77,0:12:50.47,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,待你悬吊在绞台上任自己豢养的乌鸦戏弄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.35,0:12:53.63,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就可以和平相处
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.23,0:12:59.10,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,绞台和乌鸦?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.40,0:13:00.93,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,老糊涂!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.15,0:13:05.75,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你想要什么, 灰衣甘道夫?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.89,0:13:08.66,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,让我猜猜, 是奥桑克塔的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.71,0:13:11.58,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,或者干脆是巴拉多的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.62,0:13:15.74,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,连同七王之冠和五巫之杖一起!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.62,0:13:18.97,remark,,0000,0000,0000,,*这里七王的说法意指不明,可能泛指人类英王; \N五巫指的是受梵拉派遣来到中洲协助自由人民对抗索隆的五位巫师,\N白袍萨茹曼原为这五位巫师之首
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.82,0:13:18.97,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你的背叛已让许多人失去性命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.04,0:13:21.42,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,现在更有成千上万人陷入险境
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.52,0:13:23.96,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,但你还能挽救他们, 萨茹曼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.05,0:13:26.46,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你曾是敌人的心腹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.52,0:13:29.83,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这么说你是来打探情报的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.48,0:13:32.86,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我是有些话讲给你听
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.88,0:13:41.02,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,中土的核心溃烂腐坏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.06,0:13:44.23,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,那是你未能看到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.79,0:13:49.52,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,但那巨眼看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.31,0:13:54.72,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,现在他正稳步推进
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:58.86,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,很快他就会进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:04.06,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你们全都会死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.64,0:14:09.20,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,可你是知道的, 对吗, 甘道夫?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.26,0:14:14.46,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你不会真的以为这个游侠能坐上冈多的王位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:20.65,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这个从阴影中爬出来的流浪汉永远不会加冕称王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.56,0:14:26.15,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,甘道夫会毫不犹豫地牺牲掉那些最亲近他的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.21,0:14:29.05,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,那些他宣称爱护的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.61,0:14:34.16,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我, 你叫那个半身人去送死之前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.25,0:14:37.54,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,跟他说了什么安慰的话?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.45,0:14:44.74,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你送他踏上的道路只会通向死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.77,0:14:46.91,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我听够了!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:49.35,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,射死他, 一箭射穿他的嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.41,0:14:50.91,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.53,0:14:53.67,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,下来吧, 萨茹曼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.73,0:14:55.76,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,就可以饶你不死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.76,0:14:58.05,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,省省你的同情和怜悯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:15:00.02,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.65,0:15:10.30,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,萨茹曼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.12,0:15:13.94,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你的手杖碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.19,0:15:29.04,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,格里玛, 你不需要跟着他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.83,0:15:32.45,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你以前可并不像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.50,0:15:35.55,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你也曾是罗翰的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.65,0:15:37.06,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.14,0:15:40.23,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,罗翰的一员?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.55,0:15:42.99,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,罗翰的厅堂算个什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.08,0:15:46.69,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不过是供土匪喝酒、臭气熏天的茅草马厩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:50.66,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,让乳臭未干的孩童和狗在地上打滚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.04,0:15:57.91,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,海尔姆深谷的胜利不属于你, 养马的塞奥顿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.00,0:16:02.79,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你只是伟大先祖的一个渺小后裔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.14,0:16:06.84,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,格里玛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.70,0:16:09.69,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.84,0:16:11.42,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,自由离开他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.51,0:16:14.51,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,自由? 他永远也不会自由
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:15.97,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.97,0:16:18.71,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,跪下, 无赖!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:21.63,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,萨茹曼!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.74,0:16:24.59,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你曾是敌人的心腹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.73,0:16:27.09,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,把你知道的告诉我们!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:30.61,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你先撤走你的守兵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.61,0:16:34.03,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,然后我会告诉你宿命的败亡落在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.03,0:16:37.07,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会在此充当俘虏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.57,0:17:06.50,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,传话给我们的盟友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.51,0:17:09.77,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,以及中土世界每个坚守自由的角落
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.82,0:17:13.11,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人向我们进军, 我们需要知道他进攻的地点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.17,0:17:36.12,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,萨茹曼的污秽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.29,0:17:39.87,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,荡涤殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.30,0:17:45.22,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,树木要重返故里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.31,0:17:47.51,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,小树苗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.54,0:17:49.30,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,野树丛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.30,0:17:50.74,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,皮平!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.36,0:18:01.64,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,保佑我的树皮!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.70,0:18:03.57,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,佩里格林·图克!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.61,0:18:06.11,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我来拿那个, 孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.43,0:18:08.41,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.54,0:19:04.45,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,今夜我们铭记那些抛洒热血保卫这个国家的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.65,0:19:06.88,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,向捐躯的烈士们致敬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.94,0:19:08.88,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,致敬!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.43,0:19:21.25,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不准停
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.28,0:19:22.31,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不准洒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.31,0:19:25.86,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,也不准吐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.12,0:19:28.24,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,所以这就是个饮酒比赛?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.33,0:19:32.11,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,站到最后的人赢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:37.32,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们敬点什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:38.78,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就敬胜利吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.81,0:19:40.66,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,敬胜利!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.61,0:19:55.19,rohan,,0000,0000,0000,,祝您康健, 阿拉贡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.96,0:20:25.93,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我为你高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.99,0:20:28.46,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他是个值得尊敬的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.84,0:20:31.34,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你们都是值得尊敬的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.18,0:20:38.52,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,带领人民走向胜利的并不是罗翰的塞奥顿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.55,0:20:48.61,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,别听我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.20,0:20:50.93,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你还年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.03,0:20:53.36,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚是你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.64,0:21:09.26,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,来来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.67,0:21:16.78,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,矮人们正和毛茸茸的小个子女人一起游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.10,0:21:24.09,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉到有什么不对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.42,0:21:27.91,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,手指上有轻微刺痛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.68,0:21:30.44,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这酒有点劲头
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.14,0:21:34.08,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我说过什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.11,0:21:37.49,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他酒量不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.07,0:21:46.13,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,游戏结束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.18,0:21:49.77,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}♪任你踏遍千万里\N大城小镇喝个空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.86,0:21:54.00,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}♪遍寻醇酒找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.05,0:21:58.43,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}♪遍寻醇酒找不到\N比我家乡村醪浓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.49,0:22:02.34,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}♪你自爱你的好麦酒\N豪饮一壶接一盅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.37,0:22:06.04,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}♪真正英雄配佳酿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.36,0:22:09.76,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,皮平!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.18,0:22:13.59,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}♪真正英雄配佳酿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.61,0:22:16.32,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}♪世间酒馆数绿龙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.04,0:22:21.64,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们! 我赢了!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.58,0:22:26.05,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,没有弗罗多的消息?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.29,0:22:29.34,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,没有消息, 什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.45,0:22:32.51,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们有时间等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.33,0:22:37.71,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,每过一天弗罗多都更靠近魔多一点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.30,0:22:40.42,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们能确信这一点吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.27,0:22:46.55,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你心中是怎么想的?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.03,0:22:55.66,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我想弗罗多还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.42,0:23:00.00,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.91,0:23:05.41,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊, 他还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.23,0:23:10.17,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,太冒险了, 太冒险了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.34,0:23:11.58,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.76,0:23:13.79,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他们从我们这里把它偷走了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.84,0:23:17.35,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,杀了他! 杀了他! 杀了他们两个!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.35,0:23:18.88,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.51,0:23:22.35,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,安静! 不能吵醒他们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.42,0:23:25.17,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不能现在就露馅
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.23,0:23:27.30,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,但他们知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.46,0:23:29.35,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他们知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.52,0:23:32.25,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他们怀疑我们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.54,0:23:36.89,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这是说什么呢, 我的宝贝, 亲爱的?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.07,0:23:41.11,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,斯米戈尔吓破胆了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.21,0:23:43.68,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不, 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.68,0:23:45.03,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,才不会
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.03,0:23:48.12,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,斯米戈尔恨讨厌的霍比特人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.19,0:23:52.54,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,斯米戈尔想看他们...死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.30,0:23:55.58,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.01,0:23:58.40,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,斯米戈尔以前就做过一次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.40,0:24:00.40,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他还能再做一次
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.39,0:24:06.06,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,它是我们的!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.13,0:24:08.20,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.86,0:24:12.89,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须拿到宝贝, 我们必须把它拿回来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.96,0:24:16.31,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,耐心! 耐心点, 亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.46,0:24:21.35,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,首先我们要把他们领到她那里去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.76,0:24:27.02,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们把他们领到盘旋台阶那里
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.08,0:24:29.75,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,对, 台阶, 然后呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.80,0:24:32.92,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,上, 上, 上, 上, 上台阶
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.97,0:24:39.29,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,直到我们到达隧道
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.88,0:24:42.77,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,然后他们一进去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.14,0:24:45.74,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,就出不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.78,0:24:49.15,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,她永远饿得慌
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.41,0:24:54.73,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,她永远需要喂食
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.76,0:24:56.31,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,她必须吃东西
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.36,0:24:58.61,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,但她只捉得到脏兮兮的兽人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.64,0:25:02.02,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他们尝起来可不怎么好吃, 是不是啊, 宝贝?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.06,0:25:03.53,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.95,0:25:08.35,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不好吃, 亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.76,0:25:11.48,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,她可想吃点更香甜的肉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.51,0:25:13.62,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,霍比特人的肉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.77,0:25:18.71,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,当她把骨头和空荡荡的衣服扔出来的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.80,0:25:22.19,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就能找到它了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.25,0:25:26.45,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,然后就归我了!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.20,0:25:29.83,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,归我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.92,0:25:33.18,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,对, 我们的意思就是"归我们了"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.23,0:25:36.03,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,咕噜, 咕噜
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.86,0:25:41.35,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,宝贝一定会是我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.42,0:25:46.24,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,只等霍比特人都死掉!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.36,0:25:48.27,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你这只奸诈狡猾的癞蛤蟆!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.62,0:25:53.06,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不! 不! 主人!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.10,0:25:55.51,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不行, 山姆! 别打他!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.57,0:25:58.48,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我听他亲口说的, 他要杀了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.50,0:26:02.77,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不会的! 斯米戈尔连只苍蝇都不会打
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.09,0:26:06.81,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他这个可怕的胖霍比特人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.84,0:26:08.51,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,恨斯米戈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.59,0:26:11.22,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,还编出讨厌的谎话来
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.26,0:26:14.42,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个可悲的小蛆虫! 我要把你的脑袋塞进炉子里烤!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.58,0:26:16.08,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,山姆!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.30,0:26:18.64,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,说我是骗子? 你才是骗子!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.49,0:26:21.03,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你要是把他吓跑, 我们就迷路了!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.03,0:26:23.70,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我不管! 我做不到, 弗罗多先生
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.70,0:26:25.28,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会坐等他把我们都杀掉!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.28,0:26:27.07,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会把他赶走的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.10,0:26:28.89,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是看不出来, 对吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.95,0:26:30.61,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他是个恶棍
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.37,0:26:33.52,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们光靠自己办不到的, 山姆
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.52,0:26:35.52,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,没有向导不行
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.83,0:26:38.40,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要你站在我这一边
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.50,0:26:42.04,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是站在你这边的, 弗罗多先生
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.34,0:26:46.55,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道, 山姆, 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.84,0:26:48.96,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.01,0:26:50.99,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧, 斯米戈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.25,0:28:00.91,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,现在什么时候了?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.13,0:28:04.86,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,天还没亮
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.37,0:28:14.53,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我梦见了滔天巨浪
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.53,0:28:23.23,remark,,0000,0000,0000,,*伊奥温梦到的是第二纪末年, 海水吞没努美诺尔,\N导致其覆灭的古老故事. 原著中做这个梦的人是法拉米尔
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.63,0:28:18.42,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,爬上了翠绿的土地和山丘
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.79,0:28:22.24,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我站在一处边缘
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.21,0:28:27.12,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,脚下的深渊是无尽的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.47,0:28:30.97,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我背后有亮光闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.82,0:28:34.20,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,但我无法回头
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.42,0:28:37.74,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我只能站在那里等待
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.30,0:28:42.08,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,夜晚会改变许多想法
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.46,0:28:44.56,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,睡吧, 伊奥温
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.06,0:28:47.22,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,睡吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.92,0:28:52.08,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,...趁你还能安睡
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.03,0:29:18.10,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,星星都被遮盖住了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.45,0:29:22.23,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,东边有些东西蠢蠢欲动
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.58,0:29:26.08,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,无眠的邪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.75,0:29:31.54,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的巨眼正在转动
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.90,0:29:47.09,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.23,0:29:53.78,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,皮平!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.29,0:30:02.91,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,皮平?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.09,0:30:18.69,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,皮平, 你疯了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.69,0:30:20.60,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我就想看看它
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.66,0:30:22.07,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,就再看一眼
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.10,0:30:23.98,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,放回去
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.49,0:30:36.00,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,皮平
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.79,0:30:44.08,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.38,0:30:50.72,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,皮平
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.96,0:30:55.42,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.48,0:30:57.73,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我看见你了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.49,0:31:01.96,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,皮平!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.71,0:31:19.72,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,救命! 甘道夫, 救命!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.25,0:31:23.10,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,谁来救救他!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.67,0:31:30.93,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,皮平!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.68,0:31:33.18,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,图克家的蠢货!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.36,0:31:56.10,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.53,0:32:02.08,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,甘道夫, 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.82,0:32:04.70,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.77,0:32:06.69,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你看到什么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.21,0:32:11.82,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,一棵树
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.13,0:32:14.92,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,有一棵白树
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.98,0:32:17.30,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,在一个石头庭院里
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.59,0:32:20.87,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,枯死了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.05,0:32:27.07,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,城市在燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.13,0:32:30.67,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,米纳斯提里斯? 这就是你看见的?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.05,0:32:32.61,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我看见了...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.52,0:32:38.34,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我看见了他
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.82,0:32:43.29,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我能听见他在我脑子里说话的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.32,0:32:45.39,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟他说了什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.79,0:32:47.33,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,说话!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.91,0:32:55.44,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他问我叫什么名字, 我没有回答
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.50,0:32:56.91,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他就伤了我
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.91,0:32:59.82,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,关于弗罗多和魔戒, 你告诉他什么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.20,0:33:05.46,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,皮平的眼神没有撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.08,0:33:07.90,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,是个蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.55,0:33:11.03,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不过仍然是个诚实的蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.22,0:33:14.98,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他没有告诉索隆关于弗罗多和魔戒的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.90,0:33:18.36,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的运气好得出奇
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.44,0:33:22.68,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,皮平在帕兰提尔里窥到一眼敌人的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.68,0:33:27.24,remark,,0000,0000,0000,,*帕兰提尔亦称远见石, 持有者可以互相传递信息.\N部分遗失, 部分落入索隆之手, 使用它于是成了危险的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.24,0:33:27.53,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,索隆准备攻打米纳斯提里斯城
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.72,0:33:31.26,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,海尔姆深谷的挫败告诉了我们的敌人一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.35,0:33:34.03,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他知道伊伦迪尔的继承人出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.14,0:33:36.46,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,人类不像他想象的那么软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.46,0:33:40.34,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,仍然有勇气, 还有力量, 也许足够挑战他
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.43,0:33:42.44,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,索隆惧怕这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.55,0:33:47.17,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他不敢冒险让全中洲人民在同一面旗帜下团结起来
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.95,0:33:50.46,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他要先将米纳斯提里斯夷为平地
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.52,0:33:53.71,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,以免人类的王座上重新坐上一位英王
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.90,0:33:56.06,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,如果冈多的烽火点燃
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.06,0:33:58.91,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,罗翰必须准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.15,0:34:00.82,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.52,0:34:05.99,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们为什么要千里驰援那些不肯援助我们的人?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.20,0:34:11.18,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们欠冈多什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.16,0:34:13.22,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.22,0:34:14.22,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不行!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.25,0:34:15.79,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他们必须得到警告
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.79,0:34:17.82,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他们会得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.27,0:34:23.90,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你必须取道另一处前往米纳斯提里斯
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.96,0:34:25.62,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,沿河而行
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.62,0:34:28.22,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,看向黑船
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.47,0:34:31.38,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,记住这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.50,0:34:35.32,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,如今之事既已开始, 就不能回转
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.77,0:34:39.24,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我这就奔赴米纳斯提里斯
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.24,0:34:43.72,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我不会一个人去
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.44,0:34:50.01,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,所有这些好管闲事的霍比特人里面\N佩里格林·图克, 你是最糟糕的一个
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.10,0:34:51.95,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,快点! 快点!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.37,0:34:54.93,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们去哪儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.95,0:34:56.24,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要看?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.27,0:34:59.12,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么老是非看不可呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.25,0:35:01.19,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道, 我忍不住
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.19,0:35:02.83,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你从来都忍不住
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.83,0:35:04.66,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起, 行了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.29,0:35:07.80,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我以后不会再犯了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.80,0:35:09.93,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你还没明白吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.96,0:35:12.37,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人以为魔戒在你手上
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.40,0:35:14.43,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他会四处找你的, 皮皮
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.43,0:35:16.88,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他们必须带你出去
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.31,0:35:20.20,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你呢? 你会跟我一起来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.32,0:35:23.70,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,梅利?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.77,0:35:25.21,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.57,0:35:32.13,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,米纳斯提里斯有多远?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.16,0:35:35.04,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,三天马程, 按纳芝古尔的飞行距离
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.07,0:35:38.23,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你最好指望没有那么个东西跟在我们尾巴后面
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.12,0:35:40.45,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,拿着
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.55,0:35:42.74,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,路上用
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.46,0:35:45.53,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,最后的一点长底烟叶
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.59,0:35:47.69,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你抽光了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.69,0:35:49.76,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你烟抽得太凶了, 皮平
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.76,0:35:52.32,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,但是, 但是我们很快就会见面的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.77,0:35:56.96,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.96,0:35:58.55,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.10,0:36:02.14,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道会发生什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.19,0:36:03.19,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,梅利
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.19,0:36:05.88,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,跑起来吧, 捷影, 让我们看看什么叫做十万火急
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.94,0:36:07.35,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,梅利!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.12,0:36:19.47,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,梅利!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.80,0:36:31.68,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他一直跟在我后头
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.90,0:36:33.78,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我到哪里他都跟着
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.25,0:36:36.54,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,从我们小时候起就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.54,0:36:43.30,remark,,0000,0000,0000,,*这里梅利使用的表达方式是tweens, 是托尔金仿造teens生造出来的词语,\N专门用于指称霍比特人在孩童到成人的33岁之间的少年时期
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.30,0:36:41.04,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我能把他卷进最糟糕的麻烦里
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.33,0:36:44.02,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,但我总能把他解救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.74,0:36:47.78,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,现在他走了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.28,0:36:52.50,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,就和弗罗多和山姆一样
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.88,0:36:55.73,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,关于霍比特人, 我学到一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.82,0:36:58.05,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他们是最吃苦耐劳的民族
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.08,0:36:59.83,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,也许该说一头蛮劲
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.89,0:37:01.77,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他是图克家的人
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.34,0:37:18.78,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,带她走最安全的路
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.80,0:37:21.44,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,灰港泊着一艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.47,0:37:24.88,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,等着带她渡过大海
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.23,0:37:28.89,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,暮星阿尔温最后的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.74,0:37:52.11,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪我看见夜空中星辰升起
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.32,0:38:08.28,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪如珍宝悬垂, 温柔闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.54,0:38:24.55,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪我看见夜空中星辰黯去
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.55,0:38:41.56,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪黑暗深沉星光黯淡, 刺痛心扉
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.50,0:38:37.71,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这里没有什么留给你...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.09,0:38:40.77,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,只有死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.70,0:38:49.11,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔温小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.81,0:38:51.72,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能耽搁
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.34,0:38:55.78,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.95,0:39:16.35,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我你看到了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.42,0:39:17.63,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔温
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.67,0:39:19.59,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你有预见未来的天赋
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.74,0:39:21.83,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.27,0:39:26.03,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我看向你的未来, 却看见了死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.09,0:39:28.47,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,但同样也有生机
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.19,0:39:34.48,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你看见有个孩子\N你看见了我的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.64,0:39:37.62,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,那个未来已经几乎不存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.65,0:39:39.96,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,但并非不可挽回
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.19,0:39:44.28,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么事情确定无疑
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.10,0:39:49.30,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,有些事情确定无疑
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.61,0:39:55.06,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我现在离开他
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.53,0:39:58.41,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我永远都会追悔莫及
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.21,0:40:01.54,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,是时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.86,0:40:10.59,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,一道火焰将从灰烬里苏醒
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.78,0:40:14.41,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,阴影中将会有光明闪亮
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.44,0:40:17.98,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,折断的剑刃必会焕然重生
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.90,0:40:29.00,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,无冕者终将再次称王
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.91,0:40:34.29,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,重铸那把剑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.73,0:40:37.30,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}父亲?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.16,0:40:58.68,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪为错过的曾经
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.37,0:41:13.40,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪为失落的现在
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.86,0:41:11.05,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你的手好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.00,0:41:17.66,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,精灵的生命正在离你而去
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.72,0:41:23.48,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪为永续之生
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.54,0:41:23.45,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.45,0:41:32.36,remark,,0000,0000,0000,,*埃尔隆德的子女拥有自由选择精灵或人类命运的权利,\N若阿尔温为了爱情选择了人类的命运, \N即是放弃了跟随精灵们登船前往西方不朽之地的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.36,0:41:32.81,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪为半予之爱
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.39,0:41:28.15,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是否遵从您的意愿
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.93,0:41:33.38,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,从此不再会有载我离去的航船
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.00,0:42:23.32,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们刚刚进入了冈多的疆界
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.84,0:42:37.19,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,米纳斯提里斯
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.63,0:42:40.11,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,诸王之城
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.42,0:43:12.80,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,让道!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.51,0:43:44.42,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这棵树
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.58,0:43:46.36,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,甘道夫, 甘道夫
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.36,0:43:48.80,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 冈多的白树
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.36,0:43:53.46,remark,,0000,0000,0000,,*第二纪末年努美诺尔陷落后, 伊西尔德将白树种子栽种在冈多,\N据称白树与冈多之王的命运息息相关
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.84,0:43:50.65,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,国王之树
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.68,0:43:53.50,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,然而德内索尔大人却不是国王
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.56,0:43:56.88,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他只是个摄政王, 王位的看守人
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.91,0:44:00.95,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,给我仔细听好, 德内索尔大人是博罗米尔的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.05,0:44:05.18,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,告知他心爱儿子的死讯是极不明智的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.28,0:44:08.37,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,也千万别提弗罗多或者魔戒
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.66,0:44:12.04,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,也别提到阿拉贡
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.20,0:44:17.83,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,事实上, 你最好一个字也别说, 佩里格林·图克
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.28,0:44:54.50,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,向您致敬, 埃克瑟里昂之子德内索尔\N冈多的摄政王殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.13,0:45:05.14,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我在这个黑暗的时刻前来, 带来消息与建议
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.97,0:45:09.34,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,也许你来是为了解释这个
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.98,0:45:19.96,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,也许你来是为了告诉我, 为什么我的儿子会死
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.53,0:45:33.80,quenya ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}♪泉声咽, 人何处{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.00,0:45:37.00,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,博罗米尔是为救我们而死的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.08,0:45:38.93,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,为救我和我的族亲
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.00,0:45:40.93,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他为了保护我们, 倒在了众多敌人的手下
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.93,0:45:42.41,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,皮平
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.95,0:45:51.24,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我愿以我微薄之力为您效劳
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.01,0:45:54.34,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,以此为偿
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.09,0:45:59.41,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我给你的第一道命令
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.00,0:46:03.86,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你逃脱了我的儿子没有逃脱的命运?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.11,0:46:06.83,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他是那样强大的人
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.99,0:46:10.12,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,最强大的人也会被一支箭夺去生命
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.62,0:46:13.00,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,而博罗米尔身中多箭
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.60,0:46:18.23,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,起来
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.54,0:46:20.01,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.01,0:46:23.46,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,终有一日我们可以为博罗米尔哀悼
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.63,0:46:25.77,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,但现在还不是时候
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.09,0:46:28.15,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,战争迫在眉睫
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.59,0:46:31.29,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人已经兵临城下
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.75,0:46:34.23,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,您作为摄政王, 理应担当起守城的重任
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.23,0:46:36.51,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,可冈多的军队在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.56,0:46:39.67,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,您还有盟友
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.67,0:46:42.44,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,在这场战争中, 您并非孤军作战
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.61,0:46:45.24,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,给罗翰的塞奥顿传个信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.35,0:46:47.97,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,点燃烽火
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.70,0:46:52.23,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你认为自己十分聪明, 米斯兰迪尔
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.70,0:46:55.90,remark,,0000,0000,0000,,*冈多人对甘道夫的称呼与精灵一致,\N米斯兰迪尔在辛达语中意为"灰衣圣徒"
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.41,0:46:55.91,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,然而除了诡谲伎俩, 你并无智慧可言
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.58,0:47:01.74,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为白塔的眼睛是瞎的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.92,0:47:05.11,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到的远比你知道的要多
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.11,0:47:11.26,remark,,0000,0000,0000,,*德内索尔在这里暗指他使用了存于白城的那颗帕兰提尔\N他通过它看到了许多秘密和远方的消息, 也同时被索隆所影响
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.26,0:47:08.37,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你左手将我当作抵御魔多的盾牌
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.55,0:47:11.42,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,而右手却伺机将我推翻
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.59,0:47:15.29,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道与罗翰的塞奥顿一同前来的是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.36,0:47:16.94,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.94,0:47:21.60,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经听说了这个阿拉桑之子阿拉贡
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.60,0:47:26.53,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在告诉你, 我绝不会向这个北方来的游侠低头
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.61,0:47:31.13,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,残破家族的最后血脉, 早就失去了贵族的地位
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.17,0:47:37.11,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,您的权力不是为了拒绝国王回归而给您的, 摄政王
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.49,0:47:41.84,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,冈多的统治权在我手上, 不假他人
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.84,0:47:48.35,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.50,0:47:59.45,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都成了虚妄的野心
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.56,0:48:02.80,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他甚至连悲悼之情都能用来掩饰
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.69,0:48:08.83,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这座城池已经耸立了一千年
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.55,0:48:12.53,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,如今在一个疯子的痴心妄想之下, 它就要沦陷
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.96,0:48:17.17,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,而白树, 这棵国王之树, 也再无回春之日
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.28,0:48:18.82,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么他们还在守卫着它?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.82,0:48:20.91,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,因为他们仍然抱有希望
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.94,0:48:24.25,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,苍白而微茫的希望, 希望有一天它会再次盛开
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.28,0:48:28.70,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,国王会归来, 这座城市会重返当年
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.81,0:48:31.69,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,它衰落之前的样貌
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.08,0:48:35.50,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,从西方诞生的古老智慧被弃之不顾
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.59,0:48:39.74,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,国王们制造的墓穴比活人的房子还要宏伟壮丽
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.81,0:48:44.97,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他们将死去祖先的古老姓名看得\N比自己儿子的名字还要珍贵
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.98,0:48:50.18,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,无嗣的领主坐在陈旧的厅堂里, 对着家谱沉思
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.23,0:48:55.33,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,或坐在寒冷的高塔上, 询问星辰的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.48,0:48:59.93,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,由此冈多的人民步入毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.40,0:49:03.17,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,国王的血脉断绝
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.60,0:49:06.15,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,白树枯萎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.65,0:49:10.91,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,冈多的统治权交给了血脉低微的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.91,0:49:15.00,remark,,0000,0000,0000,,*冈多的国王家系为渡海而来的努美诺尔人,\N他们因梵拉的恩赐而在寿命和智慧上均优于普通人类
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.00,0:49:23.00,remark,,0000,0000,0000,,*王族血脉断绝后, 执政的摄政王家系中仅有少量的\N(甚至没有)努美诺尔血统, 故称其"血脉低微"
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.60,0:49:23.15,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,魔多
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.19,0:49:27.05,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,没错, 它就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.79,0:49:31.88,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这个城市就坐落在魔多阴影举目可见的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.03,0:49:35.12,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,暴风雨将至
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.51,0:49:38.57,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这番气象并不属于这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.60,0:49:40.86,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这是索隆制造出来的花招
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.90,0:49:44.78,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他用翻滚的烟雾为自己的大军开道
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.82,0:49:48.13,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,魔多的兽人憎恶日光
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.20,0:49:53.88,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,所以他遮住了太阳的脸庞\N让通向战争的道路畅通无阻
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.92,0:49:57.21,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,一旦魔多的阴影触及这座城市
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.92,0:50:00.13,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,一切将会开始
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.17,0:50:02.97,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.15,0:50:04.91,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,米纳斯提里斯...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.45,0:50:07.93,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,令人印象深刻
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.96,0:50:09.04,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们下一步去哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.04,0:50:11.13,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 想要离开已经太晚了, 佩里格林
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.13,0:50:13.21,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不能离开这座城市
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.33,0:50:18.42,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须等来救援
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.18,0:50:22.82,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,现在一定快到下午茶时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.99,0:50:26.94,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,至少, 在还有下午茶的体面地方\N现在应该到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.97,0:50:31.25,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们呆的地方可不体面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.00,0:50:37.43,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,弗罗多先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.45,0:50:41.85,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.97,0:50:46.13,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,只是一个感觉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.54,0:50:51.12,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.37,0:50:58.46,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你能回去的, 你当然能
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.49,0:51:00.79,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你只是在胡思乱想罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.83,0:51:03.40,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会去而复返的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.52,0:51:06.33,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,就像毕尔博先生一样
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.83,0:51:08.95,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,等着瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.96,0:51:20.81,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这片土地以前是冈多王国的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.09,0:51:29.18,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前, 当国王仍在位的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.74,0:51:52.94,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,弗罗多先生, 看
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.29,0:51:57.04,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,国王又戴上王冠了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.96,0:52:12.42,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,过来, 霍比特们! 不能停在这里, 这边走
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.80,0:52:32.90,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我猜这就是个仪式性的职位
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.30,0:52:37.74,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说, 他们没真打算让我去打仗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.36,0:52:39.37,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.37,0:52:42.00,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在要听从摄政王的命令了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.00,0:52:45.37,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他让你怎么做你就得怎么做, 佩里格林·图克
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.43,0:52:51.66,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,荒唐的霍比特人
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.10,0:52:55.58,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,城堡守卫
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.74,0:53:06.47,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.04,0:53:18.28,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有星星了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.76,0:53:20.45,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,时间到了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.17,0:53:22.71,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.55,0:53:27.52,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,真是安静
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.22,0:53:32.46,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,现在是暴风雨前的宁静
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.78,0:53:36.37,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想参加战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.35,0:53:42.31,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,但是等待一场无法避免很快开始的战斗更加糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.86,0:53:49.99,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,还有希望吗, 甘道夫? 我是说弗罗多和山姆?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.82,0:53:53.94,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,从来就没有太多希望
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.91,0:53:58.00,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,只是愚者的希望罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.54,0:54:06.33,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的敌人已经蓄势待发
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.41,0:54:09.28,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,集中了他全部的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.34,0:54:12.91,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不止是兽人, 还有人类
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.01,0:54:16.05,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,南方的哈拉德人军团
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.01,0:54:21.91,remark,,0000,0000,0000,,*哈拉德人的字面意义为"南方人", 魔戒之战中和索隆结盟.\N他们是冈多长久以来的敌人, 早在第二纪\N 努美诺尔人在中洲大陆建立据点时双方就已对立
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.15,0:54:18.93,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,海边来的雇佣兵
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.10,0:54:21.93,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他们都响应魔多的召唤
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.93,0:54:23.39,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.67,0:54:27.94,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这将是我们所知的冈多的终结
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.02,0:54:31.96,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,最重的攻击将会落在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.36,0:54:36.92,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,如果河流被攻陷, 如果奥斯吉力亚斯的驻军失守
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.96,0:54:40.59,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这个城市面前的最后一道防线就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.70,0:54:45.15,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,但我们有白袍巫师, 这总该有点意义吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.63,0:54:52.21,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,甘道夫?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.10,0:55:00.11,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,索隆还没有派出他最致命的仆人
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.14,0:55:03.89,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他将在战争中率领魔多的军队
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.09,0:55:09.22,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,据说没有活人能杀得死他
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.29,0:55:12.61,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,安格玛的巫王
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.29,0:55:19.25,remark,,0000,0000,0000,,*纳芝古尔的头领亦称安格玛巫王, 成为戒灵之前的人类身份在原著中并未提及\N 他在第二纪接受索隆赠与人类的力量之戒, 臣服于至尊之戒成为戒灵
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.49,0:55:16.05,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你见过他的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.74,0:55:19.25,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他在风云顶上刺伤了弗罗多
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.73,0:55:28.98,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他是纳芝古尔的头领
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.01,0:55:31.55,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,九大戒灵中最强大的一个
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.58,0:55:35.25,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,米纳斯莫古尔是他的巢穴
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.55,0:55:42.01,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,死亡之城
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.35,0:55:44.45,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,非常糟糕的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.45,0:55:47.77,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,满是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.69,0:55:57.01,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,快点, 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.03,0:56:01.03,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他们会发现的, 他们会发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.19,0:56:12.73,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,过来, 过来
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.73,0:56:15.76,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,看, 我们找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.83,0:56:19.62,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,通往魔多的路
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.96,0:56:23.75,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,秘密的阶梯
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.56,0:56:26.82,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,爬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.20,0:56:48.58,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,别, 弗罗多先生!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.58,0:56:50.30,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不是那边!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.80,0:56:56.28,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,它在做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.28,0:56:57.44,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,别
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.69,0:56:59.01,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在召唤我
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.04,0:57:00.17,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,别
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.54,0:57:33.53,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,躲起来! 躲起来!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.94,0:58:19.92,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我能感觉到他的利刃
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.60,0:58:33.88,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们终于来到了这一天
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.56,0:58:38.67,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们这个时代最宏大的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.60,0:59:21.64,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,过来, 霍比特们. 我们爬, 我们必须爬
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.81,0:59:33.10,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,棋盘已经布置好
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.91,0:59:36.45,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,棋子开始移动
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.95,0:59:41.67,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,上去, 上去, 我们上台阶去
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.71,0:59:44.51,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,然后我们进隧道
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.56,0:59:47.69,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿, 隧道里有什么东西?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.63,0:59:51.35,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你听我说, 你给我仔细认真地听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.35,0:59:54.39,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,万一他出了什么事, 你就等着我找你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.44,0:59:56.08,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,只要我嗅到一丝不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.11,0:59:59.65,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,只要我脖子后面有一根汗毛竖起来, 你就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.74,1:00:02.50,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不准再偷偷摸摸, 不准再四处乱窜
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.57,1:00:05.44,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不然就滚蛋, 明白了?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.07,1:00:08.07,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我会一直盯着你
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.41,1:00:15.41,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,出了什么事吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.58,1:00:18.26,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,没事, 就是澄清点事情
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.76,1:00:27.77,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,佩里格林·图克, 小伙子, 现在有件任务交给你
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.82,1:00:31.86,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,另一个让夏尔人证明自我价值的机会
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.16,1:00:38.94,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不许让我失望
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.97,1:01:15.93,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,河那边很安静
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.18,1:01:18.39,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,兽人们正潜伏着
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.64,1:01:20.85,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,军团可能已经出动了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.82,1:01:24.52,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经向凯尔安德罗斯派去了哨兵
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.96,1:01:30.96,remark,,0000,0000,0000,,*凯尔安德罗斯是安都因河上的一个狭长的岛屿,\N位于米纳斯提里斯以北, 魔多大军若要跨越安都因河,\N这是除奥斯吉力亚斯和罗翰的南北浅滩之外唯一可行的通路
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.69,1:01:27.92,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,如果兽人们从北面攻来, 我们会得到警报
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.47,1:01:55.00,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,轻点
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.51,1:02:00.09,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,还需要十个人
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.67,1:02:23.28,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,杀了他!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.69,1:02:42.73,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他们不是从北边来的
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.56,1:02:46.97,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,到河边去, 快点, 快点, 走
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.87,1:02:49.10,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,来啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.41,1:02:53.77,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,加快速度
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.87,1:03:08.22,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,拔剑
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.96,1:04:06.39,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,拖住! 拖住他们!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.92,1:05:28.15,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.32,1:05:42.93,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,阿蒙丁
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.57,1:05:51.83,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,烽火台, 阿蒙丁的烽火台点起来了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.83,1:05:54.84,remark,,0000,0000,0000,,*阿蒙丁是距离米纳斯提里斯最近的一座烽火台
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.84,1:05:58.28,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,希望点亮了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.56,1:07:33.49,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,米纳斯提里斯的烽火台!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.49,1:07:35.57,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,烽火点燃了!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.02,1:07:39.03,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,冈多请求援助
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.16,1:07:51.31,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,而罗翰必会响应
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.49,1:07:54.52,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,召集罗翰骑士
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.15,1:08:12.34,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,在顿哈罗集结军队
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.15,1:08:17.05,remark,,0000,0000,0000,,*顿哈罗是埃多拉斯以南的一处罗翰要塞,\N位于一处悬崖顶部, 俯瞰雪界河河谷
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.46,1:08:14.59,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,集结人马, 越多越好
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.69,1:08:16.47,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,给你两天时间
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.13,1:08:18.48,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,第三天
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.48,1:08:21.89,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就向冈多进发, 奔向战场
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.17,1:08:24.73,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,-前进   -很好, 长官
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.76,1:08:26.29,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,-加姆林   -陛下
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.32,1:08:28.14,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,全速穿越里德马克
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.32,1:08:34.46,remark,,0000,0000,0000,,*里德马克是罗翰人对自己土地的称呼, 字面意义为"骑士之境"
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.17,1:08:30.38,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,召集所有体力够格的男人到顿哈罗
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.38,1:08:31.46,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.05,1:08:37.55,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你会和我们并骑吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.55,1:08:39.37,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,只到营地为止
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.37,1:08:42.92,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,宫廷女性送男人出征是一个传统
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.84,1:08:52.03,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这些人找到了自己的领袖
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.08,1:08:55.07,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他们会随着你上战场, 甚至随你奔赴死亡
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.43,1:08:57.15,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你给了我们希望
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.23,1:09:01.82,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,打扰一下
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.52,1:09:05.21,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我有一把剑
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.32,1:09:06.96,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,请您接受它
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.97,1:09:11.33,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我以微薄的力量为您效力, 塞奥顿王
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.57,1:09:17.90,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我很高兴接受你的效力
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.98,1:09:23.37,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是罗翰扈从梅利亚多克
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.79,1:09:29.52,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,骠骑之民, 嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.72,1:09:34.94,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我倒希望能聚集起一整个矮人军团, 全副武装, 令人生畏
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.72,1:09:38.58,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你的族人可能不需要长途奔袭了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.89,1:09:42.19,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我担心战争已经踏上他们自己的土地
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.89,1:09:48.89,remark,,0000,0000,0000,,*此处指魔戒之战在南方开战的同一时刻, 发生在北方的战争.\N孤山和河谷城均遭受敌袭,人类和矮人在这次战争中并肩作战
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.79,1:10:04.24,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,于是米纳斯提里斯的城墙之下...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.38,1:10:08.28,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,...将会决定我们这个时代的命运
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.90,1:10:12.61,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,是时候了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.61,1:10:16.45,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,罗翰骑士们, 你们发下了誓言
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.61,1:10:20.61,remark,,0000,0000,0000,,*这里所说"誓言"指的是"伊奥尔誓言", 承诺冈多和罗翰互为盟国, 互相援助\N 由罗翰首任国王伊奥尔和冈多第十二任摄政王契利昂缔结盟约
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.47,1:10:20.31,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,现在是兑现的时刻了, 为君王为疆土!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.10,1:11:04.83,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,法拉米尔!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.08,1:11:15.67,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪星之堡垒入敌手
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.48,1:11:14.72,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们支撑不住了, 城市已经失守
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.78,1:11:18.86,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,叫弟兄们突围, 我们撤回米纳斯提里斯
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.91,1:11:27.04,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪奥斯吉力亚斯已陷落
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.54,1:11:29.97,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,纳芝古尔
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.33,1:11:33.89,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,找掩护!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.02,1:11:36.55,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,纳芝古尔!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.43,1:11:41.59,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,退回去, 退回米纳斯提里斯!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.66,1:11:49.17,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,退回去!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.40,1:11:58.88,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,撤退! 撤退!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.91,1:12:00.79,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,逃命去吧!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.71,1:12:29.77,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,人类的时代结束了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.22,1:12:34.54,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,兽人的时代已经到来
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.98,1:12:39.08,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,继续走啊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.08,1:12:40.84,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,是纳芝古尔
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.07,1:12:43.77,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,找掩护, 大人!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.45,1:12:45.76,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,它来了!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.62,1:12:52.98,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,是米斯兰迪尔
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.01,1:12:55.07,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,是白骑士!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.84,1:13:22.66,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪光芒亮起在西方
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.70,1:13:28.11,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪白骑士到来
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.24,1:13:34.09,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪追逐至此结束
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.96,1:13:36.33,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,停!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.14,1:13:55.92,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,米斯兰迪尔
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.49,1:13:58.45,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他们突破了我们的防线
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.56,1:14:01.04,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他们占领了大桥还有河西岸
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.02,1:14:03.90,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,兽人军团正在渡河
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.90,1:14:06.11,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,就和德内索尔大人预测的一模一样
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.13,1:14:08.01,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他早就预见到这一命运了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.01,1:14:10.37,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,预见到了, 却什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.16,1:14:15.54,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,法拉米尔?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.55,1:14:21.89,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是你在路上遇见的第一个半身人
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.46,1:14:23.72,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,确实不是
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.01,1:14:27.86,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你见到了弗罗多和山姆?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.49,1:14:30.37,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里? 什么时候?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.37,1:14:32.01,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,在伊锡利恩
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.01,1:14:33.98,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不到两天之前
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.56,1:14:38.53,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,甘道夫, 他们往莫古尔山谷的那条路去了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.93,1:14:42.35,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,然后打算走奇利斯昂戈尔小道
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.57,1:14:46.36,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.11,1:14:48.64,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,出了什么事?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.89,1:14:51.65,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,法拉米尔, 全告诉我
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.20,1:14:54.24,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,把你知道的都告诉我
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.44,1:14:58.45,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你为自己的城市效力的方式?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.15,1:15:02.17,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你甘愿让它冒完全毁灭的风险?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.34,1:15:05.50,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我靠自己的判断, 做了我认为正确的事
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.78,1:15:08.46,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你认为正确的事
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.26,1:15:15.13,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你借一个愚蠢的半身人之手\N将力量之戒直接送进了魔多
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.15,1:15:23.65,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,它应该被带回城堡妥帖地收起来
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.57,1:15:26.91,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,藏起来
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.53,1:15:30.19,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,藏在黑暗幽深的地窖里
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.55,1:15:32.48,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不再使用
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.82,1:15:41.66,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,除非到了最为紧要的关头
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.13,1:15:44.16,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不会动用魔戒
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.34,1:15:47.86,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,即便米纳斯提里斯陷入浩劫, 只有我才能拯救她
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.89,1:15:52.73,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你总想表现得光明正大无可挑剔
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.76,1:15:55.09,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,就像古老时代的国王一样
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.81,1:16:00.51,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,但是博罗米尔会记得他父亲的需求
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.01,1:16:03.69,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他本会将这高贵的重礼交付予我
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.72,1:16:06.03,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,博罗米尔是不会把魔戒带给你的
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.61,1:16:09.73,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他会伸手将其据为己有, 他会堕落
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.77,1:16:10.87,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你对这事一无所知!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.87,1:16:13.18,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他会自己留着魔戒
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.13,1:16:15.87,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,当他返家之时
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.33,1:16:18.99,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你将不再认识自己的儿子
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.03,1:16:21.79,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,博罗米尔对我心怀忠诚!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.84,1:16:24.85,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,可不是什么巫师的门生!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.85,1:16:31.63,remark,,0000,0000,0000,,*德内索尔蔑称法拉米尔为"巫师的门生", 因为比起热爱战斗的博罗米尔,\N法拉米尔更热爱传说掌故, 因此一直和来访的甘道夫很亲近, 常向他学习.\N但德内索尔不喜欢甘道夫, 认为他威胁了自己的统治
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.63,1:16:33.92,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,父亲?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.56,1:16:48.29,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我的儿子
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.76,1:17:16.37,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,退下
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.64,1:17:52.63,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,小心, 主人, 小心
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.65,1:17:55.36,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这里落下去很深
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.20,1:18:01.26,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这些台阶非常危险
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.77,1:18:06.28,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧, 主人
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.03,1:18:15.36,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,到斯米戈尔这里来
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.39,1:18:23.94,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,弗罗多先生
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.85,1:18:26.20,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你, 回去!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.73,1:18:28.39,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,别碰他!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.00,1:18:35.99,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么他这么恨可怜的斯米戈尔?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.01,1:18:39.35,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,斯米戈尔对他做了什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.95,1:18:41.43,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,主人?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.12,1:18:46.63,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,主人身负沉重的负担
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.73,1:18:49.01,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,斯米戈尔知道
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.06,1:18:52.05,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,很重, 很重的负担
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.48,1:18:54.71,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,胖子不会懂
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.57,1:19:00.32,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,斯米戈尔照顾主人
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.56,1:19:03.54,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他想要它
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.99,1:19:08.06,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他需要它, 斯米戈尔从他的眼睛里看出来了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.66,1:19:12.07,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他很快就会向你要它了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.07,1:19:13.83,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,等着看吧
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.28,1:19:18.22,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,那个胖子会把它从你身边拿走
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.35,1:19:29.66,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,大军全部出动
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.92,1:19:34.58,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不拿下城市绝不停止攻击
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.68,1:19:37.02,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,把他们全杀光
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.48,1:19:41.38,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,那个巫师怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.51,1:19:45.17,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我会亲自摧毁他
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.54,1:19:50.94,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,塞奥顿的骑兵在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.12,1:19:53.20,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,罗翰的军队会来吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.83,1:19:55.49,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,米斯兰迪尔?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.17,1:20:00.50,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,勇气是你们现在最好的防御
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.84,1:20:08.71,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你在想什么, 佩里格林·图克?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.72,1:20:15.81,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,一个霍比特人能为伟大的人类首领效什么力呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.41,1:20:18.02,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你做得很好
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.31,1:20:24.49,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,慷慨的善举不该用冷淡的意见评判
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.00,1:20:28.41,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你会加入塔楼守卫的行列
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.16,1:20:32.15,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为他们找不到我合穿的制服呢
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.22,1:20:34.70,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,它曾经属于这个城市里的一个小男孩
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.83,1:20:36.51,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,一个特别愚蠢的孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.58,1:20:40.98,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他浪费了太多时间去屠龙, 而不是学习
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.00,1:20:42.11,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.11,1:20:43.92,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,对, 以前是我的
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.92,1:20:45.97,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我父亲让人给我做的
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.76,1:20:48.26,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,唔
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.38,1:20:50.39,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,那我比你小时候高点儿
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.43,1:20:54.00,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不过我现在应该没可能再长个儿了, 除非横着长
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.73,1:20:58.85,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我穿着也从来没合身过
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.94,1:21:01.77,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,博罗米尔才是家里的战士
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.67,1:21:07.30,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他们十分相像, 他和我父亲
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.28,1:21:10.82,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,骄傲
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.04,1:21:12.85,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至说得上顽固
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.00,1:21:15.84,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,但却坚强
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.04,1:21:20.03,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为你的坚强是另一种
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.84,1:21:23.34,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天你父亲会看到的
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.47,1:21:31.25,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我在此宣誓对冈多尽忠效力
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.43,1:21:33.35,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,无论和平或战争
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.53,1:21:35.76,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,活着或面临死亡
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.47,1:21:38.64,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,从...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.31,1:21:43.97,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,...从此以往
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.17,1:21:46.45,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,直到王上赦免
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.73,1:21:50.06,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,或死亡来临
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.49,1:21:52.77,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,而我不会忘记你的誓言
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.16,1:21:56.84,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,亦不会忘记给你应有的回报
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.13,1:22:06.40,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,以爱回报忠诚
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.51,1:22:09.74,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,以荣誉回报勇猛
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.76,1:22:14.68,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,以复仇回报不忠
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.73,1:22:26.88,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我们不该如此轻易地放弃外围防御
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.98,1:22:30.04,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你哥哥长期捍卫着的外围防御
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.06,1:22:31.27,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,您要让我做什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.29,1:22:35.43,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不会刀兵未动就交出佩兰诺上的河流
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.29,1:22:40.05,remark,,0000,0000,0000,,*佩兰诺平原紧邻米纳斯提里斯, 位于安都因河西岸.若索隆大军过河, \N佩兰诺平原是阻挡其进攻米纳斯提里斯的最后一道防线
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.46,1:22:37.32,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,必须重夺奥斯吉力亚斯
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.34,1:22:40.05,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,大人, 奥斯吉力亚斯的形势已经无法挽回
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.13,1:22:42.69,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,战斗当然需要付出许多代价
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.50,1:22:49.56,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这里还有带兵之人有勇气执行王上的命令吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.68,1:22:58.70,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在希望我们能掉换位置
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.89,1:23:02.53,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,死的是我, 而博罗米尔还活着
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.15,1:23:07.89,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.71,1:23:10.77,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我确有此愿
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.27,1:23:21.48,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,既然上天夺走了博罗米尔
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.54,1:23:26.42,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我会尽我所能代他效力
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.65,1:23:36.61,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,若我能回来
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.76,1:23:38.80,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,请待我好些, 父亲
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.14,1:23:44.24,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这取决于你是怎么回来的
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.18,1:25:10.01,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你想干什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.39,1:25:12.07,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,鬼鬼祟祟地开溜, 是吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.45,1:25:13.98,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,鬼鬼祟祟?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.40,1:25:17.26,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,鬼鬼祟祟?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.99,1:25:22.15,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,胖霍比特永远都这么有礼貌
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.28,1:25:27.53,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,斯米戈尔带他们走了没人知道的秘密通道
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.58,1:25:30.26,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,然后他们说"鬼鬼祟祟"
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.37,1:25:32.60,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,鬼鬼祟祟?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.52,1:25:36.21,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,真是好朋友, 对吧, 我的宝贝
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.21,1:25:37.36,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,真好, 真好
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.36,1:25:38.92,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,行了, 行了!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.34,1:25:42.61,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才吓了我一跳, 就这样
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.05,1:25:44.72,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.47,1:25:48.63,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,鬼鬼祟祟
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.01,1:25:51.54,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧, 随你怎么说
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.35,1:25:56.58,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起, 吵醒你了, 弗罗多先生
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.23,1:25:58.94,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,咱们得上路了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.31,1:26:06.05,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,天还黑着呢
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.17,1:26:07.98,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这地方一直就黑乎乎的
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.54,1:26:14.10,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,没有了!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.81,1:26:17.11,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,精灵干粮没有了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.11,1:26:18.37,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.72,1:26:20.50,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,那可是我们仅存的食物了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.26,1:26:25.84,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他拿了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.84,1:26:27.25,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是他干的!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.30,1:26:28.43,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,斯米戈尔?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.43,1:26:30.72,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不, 不, 不是可怜的斯米戈尔
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.72,1:26:33.70,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,斯米戈尔讨厌恶心的精灵干粮
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.75,1:26:37.11,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个谎话精! 你拿它干什么了?!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.15,1:26:38.84,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他根本就不吃
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.34,1:26:40.78,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能是他拿的
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.78,1:26:42.11,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.07,1:26:44.59,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.53,1:26:49.71,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他衣服上有饼干渣
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.71,1:26:51.39,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,是他拿的!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.57,1:26:53.52,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,是他拿的
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.07,1:26:58.09,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我都看见了, 主人一不注意他就往嘴里塞
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.11,1:26:59.87,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,无耻谎话!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.42,1:27:02.73,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个臭哄哄的两面派!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.91,1:27:04.49,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,-居然叫我...   -山姆!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.51,1:27:05.57,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,快住手!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.57,1:27:07.65,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,山姆!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.18,1:27:10.44,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我要杀了他!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.46,1:27:12.32,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,山姆! 不!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.67,1:27:15.30,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 我...对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.30,1:27:19.12,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是故意的, 我刚才就是...就是太生气了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.39,1:27:21.68,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,现在, 我们...我们休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.69,1:27:22.88,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.88,1:27:23.94,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.94,1:27:25.59,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你才不是没事
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.59,1:27:27.20,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你累坏了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.20,1:27:29.03,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,都怪那个咕噜姆
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.48,1:27:31.34,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,都怪这个鬼地方
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.41,1:27:33.82,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,都怪挂在你脖子上的玩意儿
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.46,1:27:38.99,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以帮点忙
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.02,1:27:41.58,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以替你拿一会儿
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.58,1:27:43.49,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,拿一会儿
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.53,1:27:45.47,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以替你拿...我可以替你拿
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.55,1:27:48.28,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,分担重负...分担重负...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.28,1:27:51.01,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,重负...重负...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.09,1:27:52.38,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,走开!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.54,1:27:54.32,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我没想自己留着
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.73,1:27:59.49,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想帮个忙
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.73,1:28:04.41,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,瞧? 瞧?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.49,1:28:07.93,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他想据为己有
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.15,1:28:09.76,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你闭嘴!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.36,1:28:12.37,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,滚! 一边去!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.41,1:28:14.00,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不, 山姆
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.55,1:28:16.11,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,该走的是你
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.87,1:28:21.58,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起, 山姆
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.01,1:28:24.63,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,可他是个骗子
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.79,1:28:27.42,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他设计让你怀疑我
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.88,1:28:30.96,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你没法再帮我了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.82,1:28:34.75,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是说真的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.08,1:28:38.69,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,回家吧
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.74,1:29:27.17,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪你必须明白
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.00,1:29:49.05,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪他肩负了两个儿子的责任
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.80,1:30:04.31,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪一份属于他自己
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.97,1:30:00.50,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,法拉米尔!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.02,1:30:02.55,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,法拉米尔!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.34,1:30:17.01,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪一份属于那永不归来之人
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.36,1:30:06.67,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲的神志已经疯狂了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.56,1:30:10.18,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,别轻率地放弃自己的生命
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.36,1:30:12.94,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我的忠诚不在此处又该在何方?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.32,1:30:15.93,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这是努美诺尔人的城市
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.01,1:30:19.94,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我很乐意献出生命来守护她的美丽
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.97,1:30:22.93,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,她的往事, 她的才学
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.46,1:30:28.68,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲爱你, 法拉米尔
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.60,1:30:32.44,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,一切结束之前, 他会记起来的
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.16,1:31:44.21,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你会唱歌吗, 霍比特阁下?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.59,1:31:47.87,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这个么...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.70,1:31:50.16,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,会
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.98,1:31:54.47,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,至少以我族人的标准而言唱得不错了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.38,1:31:58.79,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,但我们并没有适合在大厅里
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.78,1:32:01.52,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,或灾难时刻唱的歌
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.92,1:32:05.44,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你的歌为何不适合在我的大厅演唱?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.83,1:32:09.68,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,来, 给我唱一首
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.30,1:32:23.73,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}♪远离家乡
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.86,1:32:27.90,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}♪路在前方
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.98,1:32:36.55,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}♪世间道路多漫长
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.63,1:32:41.02,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}♪穿越暗影
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.32,1:32:46.04,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}♪与夜接壤
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.16,1:32:53.89,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}♪直到天空繁星闪亮
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.22,1:32:59.11,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}♪黑云暗影
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.64,1:33:05.69,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}♪雾海茫茫
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.43,1:33:10.28,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}♪终将消亡
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.15,1:33:17.28,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}♪终将
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.97,1:33:24.41,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}♪消亡
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.68,1:33:52.19,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,前进! 前进!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.31,1:33:57.52,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,前进! 前进! 前进!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.98,1:34:03.03,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,为国王让道
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.06,1:34:06.67,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,让道
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.35,1:34:10.98,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,国王来了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.19,1:34:14.50,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: 0,1:34:16.18,1:34:17.68,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,向您致敬, 陛下
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.71,1:34:19.94,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,格林博德, 有多少人?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.96,1:34:23.15,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我从西谷带了五百人过来, 陛下
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.48,1:34:26.82,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们从沼境带来了三百人, 塞奥顿王
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.24,1:34:29.02,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,来自雪界河畔的骑士在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.12,1:34:31.13,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他们还没人来, 陛下
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.30,1:34:50.32,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,只有六千人
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.41,1:34:53.74,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,还不到我预料的一半
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.79,1:34:57.61,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,六千人不足以冲破魔多的防线
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.84,1:35:01.54,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,还会有人来的
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.97,1:35:04.88,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,时间每流逝一分, 冈多失利的危险就增加一分
Dialogue: 0,1:35:04.96,1:35:08.15,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以等到早上, 到那时我们必须启程
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.14,1:35:29.27,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,马匹焦躁不安
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.73,1:35:31.63,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,人们沉默不语
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.68,1:35:34.69,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,在山影之下, 他们就会觉得不安
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.28,1:35:39.29,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,那边那条路
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.96,1:35:41.97,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,通向什么地方?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.85,1:35:46.59,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,那条路通往丁霍尔特, 是扇山下的大门
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.85,1:35:51.45,remark,,0000,0000,0000,,*丁霍尔特是连接罗翰与冈多南部的小路. 多年前,\N罗翰第二任国王的儿子巴尔多曾走上这条小路, 一去不返
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.37,1:35:50.25,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,胆敢前往那里的人没有一个生还
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.55,1:35:53.52,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,那座山很邪恶
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.55,1:36:16.18,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪带好武器来, 此路有去无回
Dialogue: 0,1:36:16.48,1:36:17.96,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,阿拉贡
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.06,1:36:20.62,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,咱们找点吃的去
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.35,1:36:38.76,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.89,1:36:42.40,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,一位真正的罗翰扈从
Dialogue: 0,1:36:46.44,1:36:47.97,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.98,1:36:51.18,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.48,1:36:53.64,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,其实没那么危险
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.22,1:36:56.37,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,刀刃还是钝的
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.28,1:37:00.77,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这可不妙, 一把钝刀可杀不了几个兽人
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.79,1:37:02.24,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.49,1:37:08.75,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,去找铁匠, 快去!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.43,1:37:12.49,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你不该鼓动他
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.09,1:37:15.09,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你不该怀疑他
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.72,1:37:17.63,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我不怀疑他的决心
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.63,1:37:19.89,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,只不过担心他的臂长
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.72,1:37:23.23,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,凭什么把梅利留在后方?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.25,1:37:25.76,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他跟你一样有足够的理由上战场
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.34,1:37:31.03,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么他不能为所爱的人而战?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.70,1:37:37.30,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟那霍比特人一样不懂战争
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.98,1:37:40.94,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,一旦恐惧战胜了他
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.20,1:37:46.09,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,一旦鲜血, 尖叫和战争的恐怖占了上风
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.62,1:37:49.32,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得他还能站起来战斗吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.38,1:37:53.04,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他会逃跑
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.13,1:37:55.30,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,而那样做完全没有错
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.33,1:38:00.87,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,战争是男人的事, 伊奥温
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.01,1:38:40.79,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我选择凡人的命运
Dialogue: 0,1:38:43.70,1:38:46.64,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我真希望我能
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.72,1:38:50.35,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,见他最后一面
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.53,1:39:02.85,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,大人?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.78,1:39:07.24,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,塞奥顿王在等您, 大人
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.17,1:39:29.85,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.88,1:39:46.44,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,埃尔隆德大人
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.61,1:39:50.15,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我谨代表一位我深爱之人前来
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.31,1:39:55.29,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔温日渐衰弱
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.06,1:40:04.30,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,在魔多肆虐的阴影下她撑不了多久
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.76,1:40:08.14,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,暮星的光芒正在消逝
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.76,1:40:12.38,remark,,0000,0000,0000,,*阿尔温赠与阿拉贡的宝石颈饰称为"暮星",但原著中并无\N电影中描述的暮星与阿尔温生命或魔戒命运息息相关的效果
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.37,1:40:12.38,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,索隆的力量越强, 她的力量就愈弱
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.53,1:40:16.22,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔温的生命已同至尊魔戒的命运系在一起
Dialogue: 0,1:40:17.02,1:40:19.78,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,阴影已降临在我们头上, 阿拉贡
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.96,1:40:21.60,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,末日到了
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.07,1:40:24.61,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是我们的末日, 是他的末日
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.41,1:40:28.84,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你奔赴战场, 但胜利无望
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.07,1:40:33.91,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,索隆的军队正向米纳斯提里斯进军, 这你是知道的
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.94,1:40:38.20,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,但暗地里他还派了另一支队伍, 要从大河上发起进攻
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.76,1:40:42.62,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,一支从南方驶来的海盗船队
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.71,1:40:45.15,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他们两天之内就能抵达
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.33,1:40:47.59,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你们人数太少, 阿拉贡
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.87,1:40:50.97,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你需要更多人手
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.43,1:40:53.21,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,没有别人了
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.04,1:40:58.83,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,山里还住着一些
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.84,1:41:09.47,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,谋杀犯
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.15,1:41:11.65,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,叛徒
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.04,1:41:16.32,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你指望他们去作战?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.40,1:41:18.23,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他们什么都不信
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.25,1:41:20.39,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,谁的命令也不听
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.44,1:41:23.97,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他们会听从冈多国王的命令
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.15,1:41:30.59,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪看啊! 西方之焰!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.59,1:41:35.72,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这是安都利尔, 西方之焰, 以纳西尔剑的残片铸成
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.12,1:41:54.44,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,索隆不会忘记伊伦迪尔之剑
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.57,1:42:13.48,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,曾经断折的宝剑将重回米纳斯提里斯
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.69,1:42:15.99,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,能够运用此剑力量之人
Dialogue: 0,1:42:16.01,1:42:20.34,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,可以召唤大地上最可怕的军队
Dialogue: 0,1:42:21.84,1:42:23.89,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,舍弃游侠的身份吧
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.02,1:42:26.99,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,成为你命定将要成为之人
Dialogue: 0,1:42:27.59,1:42:29.90,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,取道丁霍尔特
Dialogue: 0,1:42:33.26,1:42:35.77,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我将希望留给了人类{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:39.23,1:42:43.75,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}自己没有留下一分{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:33.75,1:42:45.69,remark,,0000,0000,0000,,*原文来自原著中阿拉贡的母亲在去世之前对他说的最后一句话\N为了躲避大敌的窥探, 阿拉贡幼年使用化名埃斯特尔,\N这个名字在辛达语中意思即为"希望", 在这里做双关使用
Dialogue: 0,1:42:55.69,1:42:57.45,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要这么做?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:57.83,1:43:01.26,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,战场就在东方, 你不能在开战前夕离开
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.50,1:43:05.60,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能抛下你的人民
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.78,1:43:08.09,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,伊奥温...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.54,1:43:10.40,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要你
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.95,1:43:13.69,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要跟来?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.49,1:43:17.17,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你难道不知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:26.71,1:43:29.72,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你爱的只是一道幻影, 一个念想
Dialogue: 0,1:43:33.61,1:43:36.17,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你想要的, 我没法给你
Dialogue: 0,1:43:49.48,1:43:52.60,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,从见你第一面起, 我就希望你能快乐
Dialogue: 0,1:44:12.58,1:44:14.64,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得自己要去什么地方啊?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:15.11,1:44:16.49,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这次不行
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.54,1:44:18.38,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这次你得留下, 吉穆利
Dialogue: 0,1:44:21.49,1:44:24.26,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你难道还不了解矮人有多固执吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:24.37,1:44:26.28,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你最好还是接受现实吧
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.31,1:44:28.44,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会跟你一起走, 小伙子
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.45,1:44:51.45,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:51.45,1:44:52.65,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他要去哪儿?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.01,1:44:54.41,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他要去哪儿?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:57.55,1:44:58.98,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,1:45:03.90,1:45:05.35,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,阿拉贡大人!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:06.10,1:45:08.41,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么他要在开战前夜离开?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:10.12,1:45:12.65,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他离开是因为这里已经没有希望了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:12.75,1:45:14.94,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他离开是因为他必须离开
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.02,1:45:16.73,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,来的人太少了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:16.87,1:45:19.63,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不可能击败魔多的军队
Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.57,1:45:23.04,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,1:45:23.70,1:45:25.25,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是不能
Dialogue: 0,1:45:27.79,1:45:31.83,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,然而我们迟早会在战场上见到他们
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.08,1:45:48.01,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经留下了指示
Dialogue: 0,1:45:50.43,1:45:53.48,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你将代替我统领人民
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.28,1:46:02.74,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,替我坐上金色大厅的王座
Dialogue: 0,1:46:03.78,1:46:06.15,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,如果战事不利的话
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.78,1:46:08.81,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,愿你尽量能长久保卫埃多拉斯
Dialogue: 0,1:46:10.27,1:46:13.43,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,您还希望我担起哪些别的责任, 陛下?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.99,1:46:17.40,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,责任?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.01,1:46:21.13,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,没有了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.60,1:46:31.62,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能再次微笑
Dialogue: 0,1:46:35.19,1:46:39.68,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,而不是悲悼注定殒命之人
Dialogue: 0,1:46:44.99,1:46:48.26,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你会活到世界焕然一新的那天
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.83,1:46:55.14,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,那时不再有绝望
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.64,1:47:12.08,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪前路已封
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.79,1:47:05.45,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,什么样的军队会在这种地方盘桓?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:05.70,1:47:07.46,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,被诅咒的军队
Dialogue: 0,1:47:09.57,1:47:14.41,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前, 山民曾向冈多的最后一任国王宣誓
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.11,1:47:23.52,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪这是亡者所为
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.84,1:47:18.83,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,战事起时就会赶来增援
Dialogue: 0,1:47:19.80,1:47:21.76,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,然而当战争真的来临
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.56,1:47:25.02,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,冈多迫切需要援兵时
Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.24,1:47:33.31,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪亡者守护它
Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.37,1:47:26.96,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他们却逃了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.43,1:47:30.32,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,消失在这黑魆魆的深山中
Dialogue: 0,1:47:31.87,1:47:34.11,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,于是伊西尔德诅咒他们
Dialogue: 0,1:47:34.59,1:47:41.66,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪前路已封
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.69,1:47:39.53,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,在履行誓言之前永远不得安息
Dialogue: 0,1:47:43.84,1:47:46.73,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,谁将自灰黯的暮色中召唤他们?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:47.53,1:47:49.39,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,那些被遗忘之人
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.84,1:47:52.85,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他们曾宣誓效忠之人的后裔
Dialogue: 0,1:47:52.88,1:47:55.09,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,将从北方来到此地
Dialogue: 0,1:47:55.29,1:47:56.97,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他将为情势所迫
Dialogue: 0,1:47:58.02,1:48:01.11,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他将通过大门踏上亡者之路
Dialogue: 0,1:48:19.95,1:48:23.04,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉血管里的血都要冻僵了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:28.84,1:48:30.49,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,前路已封
Dialogue: 0,1:48:31.57,1:48:33.65,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这是亡者所为
Dialogue: 0,1:48:34.23,1:48:36.04,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,亦由亡者守护
Dialogue: 0,1:48:37.02,1:48:38.55,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,前路已封
Dialogue: 0,1:48:49.84,1:48:51.27,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,布瑞戈!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.83,1:48:57.02,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不怕死
Dialogue: 0,1:49:09.80,1:49:12.05,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 这种事我可没听过
Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.45,1:49:17.04,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,精灵都敢进地下, 矮人反倒不敢?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.39,1:49:18.55,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,噢
Dialogue: 0,1:49:18.72,1:49:21.56,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 我还真没听过这种事呢
Dialogue: 0,1:49:36.57,1:49:38.60,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须轻装全速前进
Dialogue: 0,1:49:39.07,1:49:40.88,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这段路途可不短
Dialogue: 0,1:49:41.13,1:49:44.29,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,到达目的地后, 人和马必须还有力气作战
Dialogue: 0,1:49:49.50,1:49:52.75,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,小个子霍比特人可不适合上战场, 梅利亚多克先生
Dialogue: 0,1:49:52.84,1:49:55.01,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我的朋友们都上战场了
Dialogue: 0,1:49:55.01,1:49:57.02,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我留下来就可丢脸了
Dialogue: 0,1:49:57.05,1:49:59.17,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,到米纳斯提里斯要连着奔驰三天三夜
Dialogue: 0,1:49:59.20,1:50:02.11,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我的骑士们不能带着你这个负担上路
Dialogue: 0,1:50:02.72,1:50:04.72,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我想战斗
Dialogue: 0,1:50:05.40,1:50:06.95,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我不多说了
Dialogue: 0,1:50:24.27,1:50:25.92,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:50:27.68,1:50:28.99,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,1:50:29.21,1:50:31.34,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,整队! 出发!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:31.75,1:50:34.56,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,整队! 出发!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:38.04,1:50:39.21,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,前进!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:39.45,1:50:41.98,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,向冈多前进!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:24.02,1:51:25.52,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,是什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:26.12,1:51:27.58,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你看见什么了?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:27.73,1:51:29.56,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到有人的影子
Dialogue: 0,1:51:32.48,1:51:34.00,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,还有马
Dialogue: 0,1:51:34.73,1:51:35.84,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:36.09,1:51:38.93,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,像云絮一样的苍白旗帜
Dialogue: 0,1:51:41.36,1:51:43.54,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,高举的长矛
Dialogue: 0,1:51:44.32,1:51:47.65,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,就好像冬天里浓雾包裹的灌木丛
Dialogue: 0,1:51:48.91,1:51:50.74,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,亡者就跟在我们身后
Dialogue: 0,1:51:52.29,1:51:54.05,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他们已受召而来
Dialogue: 0,1:51:54.58,1:51:56.04,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,亡者?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:56.67,1:51:58.12,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,受召?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:58.92,1:52:00.67,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,1:52:04.01,1:52:05.57,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,1:52:06.63,1:52:08.55,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,好得很, 莱戈拉斯!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:46.47,1:52:48.08,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,别往下看
Dialogue: 0,1:53:40.52,1:53:45.64,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁擅闯我的领地?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:49.43,1:53:51.92,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,一个你们即将效忠之人
Dialogue: 0,1:53:54.58,1:54:00.20,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,亡者不允许生者通过此地
Dialogue: 0,1:54:00.28,1:54:02.83,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你会允许我通过
Dialogue: 0,1:54:26.44,1:54:29.81,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,前路已封
Dialogue: 0,1:54:31.02,1:54:35.45,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这是亡者所为
Dialogue: 0,1:54:35.96,1:54:39.75,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,亦由亡者守护
Dialogue: 0,1:54:49.21,1:54:52.02,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,前路已封
Dialogue: 0,1:54:53.98,1:54:56.59,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你们将葬身此处
Dialogue: 0,1:55:00.47,1:55:03.56,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我召唤你前来履行誓言
Dialogue: 0,1:55:03.79,1:55:08.60,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,只有冈多之王才能对我下令
Dialogue: 0,1:55:14.38,1:55:16.48,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,王室血脉早已断绝
Dialogue: 0,1:55:19.17,1:55:21.10,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,如今已寻回了
Dialogue: 0,1:55:29.18,1:55:30.69,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,为我们而战
Dialogue: 0,1:55:30.84,1:55:33.02,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,重获荣誉
Dialogue: 0,1:55:37.61,1:55:39.04,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你们意下如何?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:51.11,1:55:52.59,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你们意下如何?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:53.40,1:55:55.25,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你这是浪费时间, 阿拉贡
Dialogue: 0,1:55:55.43,1:55:58.74,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他们活着的时候都不讲荣誉, 现在死了就更不稀罕了
Dialogue: 0,1:55:59.09,1:56:01.23,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我乃伊西尔德的后裔
Dialogue: 0,1:56:02.18,1:56:03.79,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,为我而战
Dialogue: 0,1:56:04.74,1:56:08.20,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我将视你们的誓言已得践行
Dialogue: 0,1:56:12.22,1:56:13.82,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你们意下如何?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:21.93,1:56:24.09,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我绝无虚言!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:24.51,1:56:28.65,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,战斗, 我就让你们这些行尸走肉得到解脱!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:29.98,1:56:31.57,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你们意下如何?!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:34.65,1:56:37.29,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,站住, 你们这些叛徒!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:04.64,1:57:05.79,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,快出去!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:26.92,1:57:28.28,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,莱戈拉斯!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:29.71,1:57:30.99,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,快跑!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:37.31,1:58:39.02,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们参战
Dialogue: 0,1:58:50.03,1:58:52.39,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,打开大门! 快!
Dialogue: 0,1:59:23.40,1:59:25.24,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,快! 快点!
Dialogue: 0,1:59:39.24,1:59:40.60,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,法拉米尔!
Dialogue: 0,1:59:41.80,1:59:44.69,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,别说他已经阵亡了
Dialogue: 0,1:59:46.21,1:59:48.00,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他们寡不敌众
Dialogue: 0,1:59:48.25,1:59:49.91,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,无人生还
Dialogue: 0,1:59:50.56,1:59:52.37,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,恐惧
Dialogue: 0,1:59:53.14,1:59:55.88,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这城市中恐惧丛生
Dialogue: 0,1:59:58.56,2:00:01.17,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,让咱帮他们解脱吧
Dialogue: 0,2:00:01.35,2:00:03.28,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,把囚犯都放出来
Dialogue: 0,2:00:03.31,2:00:04.74,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,投石器准备!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:18.59,2:00:21.57,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我的儿子们都死了
Dialogue: 0,2:00:23.11,2:00:25.46,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我的血脉已经断绝
Dialogue: 0,2:00:28.90,2:00:30.26,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他还活着!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:30.31,2:00:33.72,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,摄政王家族已衰亡
Dialogue: 0,2:00:33.75,2:00:35.63,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他需要治疗, 大人
Dialogue: 0,2:00:36.30,2:00:38.66,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我的血脉已经断绝!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:40.45,2:00:42.08,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,大人!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:56.05,2:00:57.48,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,罗翰...
Dialogue: 0,2:00:58.54,2:01:00.65,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,抛弃了我们
Dialogue: 0,2:01:15.45,2:01:18.31,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,塞奥顿背叛了我
Dialogue: 0,2:01:29.68,2:01:31.56,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,别管你们的职责了!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:32.52,2:01:36.44,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,逃吧! 逃命去吧!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:46.67,2:01:48.12,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,准备迎战!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:48.75,2:01:51.83,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,快, 士兵们! 到城墙那去! 保卫城墙!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:53.09,2:01:54.52,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这边!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:55.71,2:01:57.66,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,回到位置上去!
Dialogue: 0,2:02:08.89,2:02:11.84,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,把这些肮脏的野兽送入深渊
Dialogue: 0,2:02:21.60,2:02:23.38,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,站在原地别动
Dialogue: 0,2:02:39.99,2:02:41.87,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要更多石头! 他们...
Dialogue: 0,2:02:41.90,2:02:43.23,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,小心!
Dialogue: 0,2:02:43.71,2:02:45.94,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,到下面那一层去, 快去!
Dialogue: 0,2:02:48.00,2:02:49.50,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,再快点, 士兵们!
Dialogue: 0,2:03:13.47,2:03:19.98,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪阴影的碎片
Dialogue: 0,2:03:20.26,2:03:27.77,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪九戒灵降临
Dialogue: 0,2:03:27.98,2:03:36.33,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪带翼的死神
Dialogue: 0,2:03:36.68,2:03:45.09,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪将吞噬一切
Dialogue: 0,2:03:46.16,2:03:55.58,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪吞噬整个世间
Dialogue: 0,2:03:57.48,2:04:03.51,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪从生中撕裂
Dialogue: 0,2:03:58.71,2:04:00.34,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,顶住攻击!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:00.34,2:04:02.21,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,别被恐惧压垮
Dialogue: 0,2:04:02.25,2:04:05.34,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,坚守位置! 坚持战斗!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:05.69,2:04:14.18,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪御恶风而行
Dialogue: 0,2:04:14.78,2:04:23.15,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪九戒灵降临
Dialogue: 0,2:04:46.41,2:04:48.00,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,别射塔楼!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:48.17,2:04:51.36,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,射巨怪! 杀死巨怪!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:51.66,2:04:53.59,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,击垮他们!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:28.92,2:05:31.06,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,把他们揍回去!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:31.13,2:05:32.71,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,佩里格林·图克!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:33.79,2:05:35.42,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,回城堡去!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:35.42,2:05:37.15,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他们叫我们出来战斗
Dialogue: 0,2:05:52.94,2:05:55.19,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是一个霍比特人该待的地方
Dialogue: 0,2:06:21.04,2:06:23.08,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是城堡守卫
Dialogue: 0,2:06:23.13,2:06:24.91,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,现在回去, 到山上去, 快
Dialogue: 0,2:06:24.98,2:06:26.14,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,快!
Dialogue: 0,2:06:37.70,2:06:40.52,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你们在做什么? 一群没用的废物
Dialogue: 0,2:06:40.54,2:06:42.90,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,城门太结实了, 撞不开
Dialogue: 0,2:06:49.10,2:06:51.61,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,回去继续给我砸
Dialogue: 0,2:06:51.61,2:06:53.51,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,可什么也砸不开那门
Dialogue: 0,2:06:56.58,2:06:58.58,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,戈隆德槌砸得开
Dialogue: 0,2:06:58.58,2:07:07.57,remark,,0000,0000,0000,,*佩兰诺平原之战上使用的戈隆德攻城槌据称有一百英尺长,\N由黑铁打造, 形似狼头. 戈隆德槌的名字直接来源于\N第一纪元时魔苟斯使用过的武器, 亦称地底之锤
Dialogue: 0,2:07:02.27,2:07:04.78,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,把狼首槌带过来
Dialogue: 0,2:07:07.64,2:07:13.09,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,戈隆德! 戈隆德! 戈隆德! 戈隆德!
Dialogue: 0,2:07:13.46,2:07:17.55,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,戈隆德! 戈隆德! 戈隆德!
Dialogue: 0,2:07:19.11,2:07:23.05,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,戈隆德! 戈隆德! 戈隆德!
Dialogue: 0,2:07:23.23,2:07:26.96,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,戈隆德! 戈隆德! 戈隆德!
Dialogue: 0,2:07:27.27,2:07:31.41,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,戈隆德! 戈隆德! 戈隆德!
Dialogue: 0,2:07:31.66,2:07:35.67,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,戈隆德! 戈隆德! 戈隆德!
Dialogue: 0,2:07:56.50,2:07:58.21,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不许再往前走了
Dialogue: 0,2:08:01.52,2:08:04.23,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你们不得进入冈多
Dialogue: 0,2:08:04.91,2:08:07.47,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁, 竟敢挡我们的路?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:07.49,2:08:11.81,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,莱戈拉斯, 贴着水手长的耳朵射一箭警告他们
Dialogue: 0,2:08:13.21,2:08:15.12,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准点
Dialogue: 0,2:08:21.27,2:08:23.85,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样, 没错, 我们可警告过你
Dialogue: 0,2:08:24.10,2:08:26.26,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,准备来人登船吧
Dialogue: 0,2:08:27.82,2:08:29.15,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,登船?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:29.17,2:08:31.63,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,就凭你们, 连军队都没有吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:32.56,2:08:34.04,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,有这支军队
Dialogue: 0,2:08:51.38,2:08:53.21,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,到里边去
Dialogue: 0,2:08:55.27,2:08:57.10,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么地方?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:01.27,2:09:04.70,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,主人必须进到隧道里边去
Dialogue: 0,2:09:06.11,2:09:09.92,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,现在站在门口, 我就不想进去了
Dialogue: 0,2:09:12.21,2:09:14.44,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这是唯一的一条路
Dialogue: 0,2:09:16.70,2:09:18.30,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,要么进去
Dialogue: 0,2:09:19.38,2:09:21.12,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,要么回去
Dialogue: 0,2:09:24.33,2:09:26.46,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能回去
Dialogue: 0,2:09:39.26,2:09:40.46,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么味道?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:40.46,2:09:41.99,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,兽人的臭味
Dialogue: 0,2:09:42.02,2:09:44.75,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,兽人有时候会来这里
Dialogue: 0,2:09:50.30,2:09:51.86,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,2:09:57.10,2:09:58.53,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这边走
Dialogue: 0,2:10:01.69,2:10:03.60,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,斯米戈尔?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:04.45,2:10:06.21,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这边
Dialogue: 0,2:10:15.09,2:10:17.73,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这黏乎乎的是什么?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:18.38,2:10:20.44,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你一会就知道了
Dialogue: 0,2:10:20.91,2:10:22.90,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 是呀
Dialogue: 0,2:10:23.35,2:10:25.86,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,一会就知道了
Dialogue: 0,2:10:35.42,2:10:36.92,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,斯米戈尔?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:38.45,2:10:39.86,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,斯米戈尔!
Dialogue: 0,2:10:42.29,2:10:44.48,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,斯米戈尔!
Dialogue: 0,2:10:53.64,2:10:55.17,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,山姆
Dialogue: 0,2:12:35.64,2:12:37.95,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,而你, 弗罗多·巴金斯
Dialogue: 0,2:12:37.98,2:12:42.79,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我赠与你伊伦迪尔之光, 这是我们最挚爱的星辰
Dialogue: 0,2:12:44.05,2:12:47.56,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,愿它在黑暗中为你带来光明
Dialogue: 0,2:12:47.59,2:12:51.15,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,纵使所有希望都已泯灭
Dialogue: 0,2:12:51.25,2:12:55.17,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fn楷体}致敬伊伦迪尔! 最明亮的星辰!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,2:14:07.49,2:14:10.82,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,淘气的小苍蝇
Dialogue: 0,2:14:10.85,2:14:14.56,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,为啥哭哭啼啼?
Dialogue: 0,2:14:14.66,2:14:18.10,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,被困在蛛网里
Dialogue: 0,2:14:18.13,2:14:21.25,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,很快就要被...
Dialogue: 0,2:14:21.44,2:14:22.99,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉啦
Dialogue: 0,2:15:00.33,2:15:03.14,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,宝贝逃出来过, 是不是?
Dialogue: 0,2:15:03.24,2:15:05.15,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这次可不行
Dialogue: 0,2:15:05.18,2:15:06.91,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这次可不行!
Dialogue: 0,2:15:06.91,2:15:08.41,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不!
Dialogue: 0,2:15:15.31,2:15:18.88,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我们干的, 不是我们干的!
Dialogue: 0,2:15:19.10,2:15:21.99,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,斯米戈尔不会伤害主人
Dialogue: 0,2:15:21.99,2:15:23.95,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们发了誓的
Dialogue: 0,2:15:23.95,2:15:26.28,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你必须相信我们
Dialogue: 0,2:15:26.36,2:15:28.49,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,是宝贝的缘故
Dialogue: 0,2:15:28.59,2:15:32.75,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,宝贝逼我们这么干的
Dialogue: 0,2:15:50.42,2:15:53.08,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,斯米戈尔, 我必须销毁它
Dialogue: 0,2:16:02.41,2:16:05.25,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我必须销毁它, 为了我也为了你
Dialogue: 0,2:16:15.69,2:16:17.14,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不行!
Dialogue: 0,2:16:40.21,2:16:42.41,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,山姆, 我真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,2:16:47.16,2:16:49.26,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,2:17:15.66,2:17:19.98,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这项任务注定属于你, 夏尔的弗罗多
Dialogue: 0,2:17:21.64,2:17:24.17,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你办不到的话
Dialogue: 0,2:17:25.25,2:17:27.06,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,那就没人可以了
Dialogue: 0,2:18:00.41,2:18:03.02,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,探子回报说米纳斯提里斯被包围了
Dialogue: 0,2:18:03.12,2:18:05.25,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,底层已经燃起大火
Dialogue: 0,2:18:06.03,2:18:08.49,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,四处都有敌军进袭
Dialogue: 0,2:18:08.66,2:18:10.26,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们时间紧迫
Dialogue: 0,2:18:10.27,2:18:11.75,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,准备出发!
Dialogue: 0,2:18:11.77,2:18:13.68,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,振作起来, 梅利
Dialogue: 0,2:18:13.88,2:18:15.79,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,很快就会结束的
Dialogue: 0,2:18:16.77,2:18:18.32,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,2:18:18.90,2:18:21.43,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,您既美丽又勇敢
Dialogue: 0,2:18:21.84,2:18:23.79,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,有许多活下去的理由
Dialogue: 0,2:18:25.75,2:18:27.66,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,还有许多爱着你的人
Dialogue: 0,2:18:30.77,2:18:33.50,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道现在离开已经太晚
Dialogue: 0,2:18:34.23,2:18:36.94,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道心存希望也多半无济于事
Dialogue: 0,2:18:38.37,2:18:42.04,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我真是个能够成就伟业的罗翰骑士就好了
Dialogue: 0,2:18:42.06,2:18:44.55,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,可我不是
Dialogue: 0,2:18:45.27,2:18:46.73,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是个霍比特人
Dialogue: 0,2:18:49.99,2:18:52.40,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道我没法拯救中洲
Dialogue: 0,2:18:55.81,2:18:58.07,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我只想帮帮我的朋友们
Dialogue: 0,2:19:00.18,2:19:01.43,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,弗罗多
Dialogue: 0,2:19:02.54,2:19:03.84,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,山姆
Dialogue: 0,2:19:05.88,2:19:07.10,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,皮平
Dialogue: 0,2:19:09.36,2:19:12.68,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我想再见见他们, 这比一切都重要
Dialogue: 0,2:19:16.64,2:19:18.62,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,准备出发!
Dialogue: 0,2:19:19.05,2:19:20.50,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,加快速度
Dialogue: 0,2:19:20.68,2:19:22.59,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们彻夜骑行
Dialogue: 0,2:19:38.77,2:19:40.18,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,前往战场
Dialogue: 0,2:19:40.35,2:19:41.61,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,前往战场
Dialogue: 0,2:20:04.82,2:20:06.23,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,回门口去!
Dialogue: 0,2:20:06.88,2:20:08.38,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,快!
Dialogue: 0,2:20:28.89,2:20:32.93,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我乃安纳里翁家族的摄政王
Dialogue: 0,2:20:33.70,2:20:36.01,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我以此名行走
Dialogue: 0,2:20:37.24,2:20:40.08,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,亦将以此名沉睡
Dialogue: 0,2:20:46.40,2:20:48.43,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,冈多已经陷落
Dialogue: 0,2:20:49.01,2:20:52.25,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,人类再无希望
Dialogue: 0,2:20:52.25,2:20:58.32,remark,,0000,0000,0000,,*白树与冈多之王的命运息息相关, 有预言提及\N当白树再次开花之日, 即是国王回归之时
Dialogue: 0,2:21:07.45,2:21:09.61,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,愚人为何奔逃?
Dialogue: 0,2:21:11.59,2:21:14.38,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,尽早死去更好
Dialogue: 0,2:21:16.76,2:21:18.82,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们必有一死
Dialogue: 0,2:21:31.04,2:21:34.38,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,德内索尔和法拉米尔不需要坟墓
Dialogue: 0,2:21:35.23,2:21:40.70,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不需要亡者漫长不朽的沉睡
Dialogue: 0,2:21:41.43,2:21:46.22,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们应像古时的异族君主般投身火海
Dialogue: 0,2:21:50.19,2:21:52.07,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,拿木柴和油来
Dialogue: 0,2:21:54.88,2:21:56.19,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,稳住
Dialogue: 0,2:21:56.39,2:21:57.82,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,稳住
Dialogue: 0,2:22:12.85,2:22:15.33,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你们是冈多的战士
Dialogue: 0,2:22:15.66,2:22:20.05,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,无论门外进来什么, 你们都要坚守阵地
Dialogue: 0,2:22:26.10,2:22:27.18,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,快跑!
Dialogue: 0,2:22:29.41,2:22:31.27,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,齐射!
Dialogue: 0,2:22:31.87,2:22:33.33,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,放箭!
Dialogue: 0,2:24:26.90,2:24:29.08,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,快放开他, 你这恶棍
Dialogue: 0,2:24:30.64,2:24:32.19,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,放开他!
Dialogue: 0,2:24:33.80,2:24:36.06,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不准你再碰他
Dialogue: 0,2:24:39.10,2:24:40.85,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,来做个了结吧
Dialogue: 0,2:26:30.74,2:26:31.97,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,退后!
Dialogue: 0,2:26:43.21,2:26:44.56,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,弗罗多先生
Dialogue: 0,2:26:54.05,2:26:55.50,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,哦不
Dialogue: 0,2:26:56.21,2:26:57.44,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,弗罗多
Dialogue: 0,2:26:58.42,2:26:59.80,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,弗罗多先生
Dialogue: 0,2:27:04.89,2:27:06.24,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒
Dialogue: 0,2:27:10.03,2:27:11.92,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,别丢下我一个人
Dialogue: 0,2:27:14.00,2:27:16.03,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,别去我跟不上的地方
Dialogue: 0,2:27:20.70,2:27:21.98,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒
Dialogue: 0,2:27:28.70,2:27:30.49,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,别睡过去
Dialogue: 0,2:27:33.07,2:27:34.45,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,别死掉
Dialogue: 0,2:27:53.62,2:27:55.65,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你这杂碎回来了啊!
Dialogue: 0,2:28:04.69,2:28:06.75,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么?
Dialogue: 0,2:28:07.35,2:28:10.53,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来像是希洛布在寻开心
Dialogue: 0,2:28:07.35,2:28:16.25,remark,,0000,0000,0000,,*大蜘蛛名为希洛布, 即咕噜姆口中的“她”. 一般认为\N中洲的蜘蛛均为古时毁去双圣树的乌戈利安特的后代
Dialogue: 0,2:28:12.12,2:28:14.55,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,她又杀了一个吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:28:14.83,2:28:16.31,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,2:28:19.49,2:28:21.85,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙还没死
Dialogue: 0,2:28:21.88,2:28:23.53,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,没死?
Dialogue: 0,2:28:24.24,2:28:26.22,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,她用刺针戳了他
Dialogue: 0,2:28:26.22,2:28:29.66,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他就会像没骨头的鱼一样软
Dialogue: 0,2:28:30.41,2:28:33.39,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,然后她就能随意享用
Dialogue: 0,2:28:33.52,2:28:35.63,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,她就喜欢这么吃东西
Dialogue: 0,2:28:35.68,2:28:37.56,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,新鲜的血肉
Dialogue: 0,2:28:37.89,2:28:39.74,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,把他抬到塔里去!
Dialogue: 0,2:28:43.73,2:28:45.84,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,山姆怀斯, 你这笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,2:28:45.87,2:28:48.74,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这杂碎再过一两个钟头就能醒
Dialogue: 0,2:28:48.78,2:28:51.59,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,到时候他会希望自己没被生出来
Dialogue: 0,2:29:15.40,2:29:18.21,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他的灵魂之所已崩塌
Dialogue: 0,2:29:19.82,2:29:21.50,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他正在燃烧
Dialogue: 0,2:29:22.35,2:29:23.90,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,已经在燃烧了
Dialogue: 0,2:29:24.06,2:29:25.69,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他还没死
Dialogue: 0,2:29:26.39,2:29:28.30,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他还没死呢!
Dialogue: 0,2:29:30.41,2:29:32.09,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不! 不!
Dialogue: 0,2:29:32.37,2:29:34.80,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不! 不!
Dialogue: 0,2:29:34.85,2:29:36.81,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他还没死呢!
Dialogue: 0,2:29:37.21,2:29:39.19,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,再会, 帕拉丁之子佩里格林
Dialogue: 0,2:29:39.19,2:29:40.87,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不! 不!
Dialogue: 0,2:29:40.90,2:29:43.88,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我解除你的职务
Dialogue: 0,2:29:45.16,2:29:49.35,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,现在离开, 找个最合意的方式去死吧
Dialogue: 0,2:29:51.96,2:29:54.00,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,往木柴上倒油!
Dialogue: 0,2:29:55.95,2:29:57.84,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,士兵, 快点! 快动手!
Dialogue: 0,2:29:58.34,2:29:59.64,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,快去那边! 快去!
Dialogue: 0,2:29:59.64,2:30:01.02,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,甘道夫!
Dialogue: 0,2:30:01.90,2:30:03.56,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,甘道夫在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,2:30:04.49,2:30:05.82,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,甘道夫!
Dialogue: 0,2:30:11.01,2:30:12.49,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,撤退!
Dialogue: 0,2:30:14.55,2:30:16.46,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他们攻进城里了!
Dialogue: 0,2:30:16.51,2:30:19.52,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,退到第二层!
Dialogue: 0,2:30:23.26,2:30:25.24,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,带女人和孩子离开!
Dialogue: 0,2:30:25.24,2:30:26.94,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,带他们离开!
Dialogue: 0,2:30:27.02,2:30:28.70,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,撤退!
Dialogue: 0,2:30:29.30,2:30:30.93,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,快, 快走
Dialogue: 0,2:30:30.98,2:30:32.97,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,进城去
Dialogue: 0,2:30:33.02,2:30:35.15,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,挡路的都杀掉
Dialogue: 0,2:30:35.15,2:30:43.21,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪九戒灵御恶风降临
Dialogue: 0,2:30:43.21,2:30:45.01,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,杀掉他们!
Dialogue: 0,2:30:45.15,2:30:53.03,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪带翼的死神
Dialogue: 0,2:30:53.92,2:30:59.99,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪将吞噬一切
Dialogue: 0,2:30:59.99,2:31:06.07,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪吞噬整个世间
Dialogue: 0,2:31:06.07,2:31:09.15,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,战斗! 战斗到最后一人!
Dialogue: 0,2:31:09.18,2:31:10.66,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,为活命而战斗!
Dialogue: 0,2:31:10.68,2:31:12.19,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,甘道夫!
Dialogue: 0,2:31:16.33,2:31:17.61,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,甘道夫!
Dialogue: 0,2:31:17.66,2:31:19.94,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,德内索尔他疯了!
Dialogue: 0,2:31:20.52,2:31:22.65,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他要活活烧死法拉米尔!
Dialogue: 0,2:31:22.73,2:31:23.88,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,上来!
Dialogue: 0,2:31:23.98,2:31:25.04,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,快点!
Dialogue: 0,2:31:31.61,2:31:33.29,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,回到深渊里去
Dialogue: 0,2:31:34.65,2:31:38.06,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,一无所有的虚空在等着你和你的主人
Dialogue: 0,2:31:38.11,2:31:44.28,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道死亡已经近在眼前了吗, 老头子?
Dialogue: 0,2:31:44.76,2:31:48.70,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,现在是我说了算
Dialogue: 0,2:31:58.89,2:32:00.22,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,甘道夫!
Dialogue: 0,2:32:09.45,2:32:12.34,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你失败了
Dialogue: 0,2:32:13.69,2:32:17.68,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,人类的世界即将毁灭
Dialogue: 0,2:33:15.78,2:33:17.36,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,勇敢些, 梅利
Dialogue: 0,2:33:17.41,2:33:19.44,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,为了我们的朋友, 勇敢些
Dialogue: 0,2:33:23.25,2:33:26.62,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,列队, 你们这些蛆虫, 列队!
Dialogue: 0,2:33:26.64,2:33:29.98,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,长矛在前, 弓箭在后
Dialogue: 0,2:33:38.06,2:33:45.01,remark,,0000,0000,0000,,*伊奥雷德是罗翰的一种军事编制, 指一支受过整套\N作战训练的骑兵, 一个伊奥雷德的人数应当不少于120人
Dialogue: 0,2:33:37.88,2:33:41.25,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,伊奥墨, 带领你的那支伊奥雷德骑兵从左翼进袭
Dialogue: 0,2:33:41.30,2:33:42.58,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,侧翼准备
Dialogue: 0,2:33:42.63,2:33:45.54,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,加姆林, 跟随王旗从中路冲锋
Dialogue: 0,2:33:45.56,2:33:49.45,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,格林博德, 过墙之后带领你的人马向右冲
Dialogue: 0,2:33:49.48,2:33:52.16,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,前进! 不惧黑暗!
Dialogue: 0,2:33:52.49,2:33:56.05,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,奋起, 奋起! 塞奥顿的骑士们!
Dialogue: 0,2:33:56.50,2:33:58.99,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,长矛当震响
Dialogue: 0,2:33:59.04,2:34:01.62,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,圆盾当迸裂
Dialogue: 0,2:34:01.92,2:34:03.88,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,此日拔剑
Dialogue: 0,2:34:03.93,2:34:05.56,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,血染疆场
Dialogue: 0,2:34:05.71,2:34:09.15,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,迎接初升朝阳!
Dialogue: 0,2:34:17.08,2:34:21.42,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不管发生什么, 跟紧我, 我会照顾你
Dialogue: 0,2:34:27.79,2:34:29.58,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,冲锋!
Dialogue: 0,2:34:31.23,2:34:33.19,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,冲锋!
Dialogue: 0,2:34:33.99,2:34:36.98,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,冲锋! 冲向毁灭
Dialogue: 0,2:34:37.08,2:34:40.69,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,冲向世界尽头!
Dialogue: 0,2:34:41.75,2:34:43.58,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,杀!
Dialogue: 0,2:34:43.68,2:34:46.21,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,杀!
Dialogue: 0,2:34:46.66,2:34:47.87,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,杀!
Dialogue: 0,2:34:47.92,2:34:50.20,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,杀!
Dialogue: 0,2:34:50.33,2:34:51.36,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,杀!
Dialogue: 0,2:34:51.41,2:34:52.64,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,杀!
Dialogue: 0,2:34:52.71,2:34:53.72,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,杀!
Dialogue: 0,2:34:53.77,2:34:56.10,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,杀!
Dialogue: 0,2:35:01.14,2:35:04.00,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,前进, 伊欧子嗣!
Dialogue: 0,2:35:46.64,2:35:48.35,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,放箭!
Dialogue: 0,2:35:52.34,2:35:53.92,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,杀!
Dialogue: 0,2:35:57.63,2:35:59.31,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,冲锋!
Dialogue: 0,2:35:59.36,2:36:00.99,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,任意放箭!
Dialogue: 0,2:36:58.46,2:37:01.37,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,在我们身上点起火
Dialogue: 0,2:37:19.18,2:37:21.22,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,停止这疯狂之举!
Dialogue: 0,2:37:25.36,2:37:29.32,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,也许你能在战场上维持一日的胜利
Dialogue: 0,2:37:30.15,2:37:34.12,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,但若想抵挡东方崛起的力量
Dialogue: 0,2:37:34.22,2:37:37.13,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,绝无胜利可言
Dialogue: 0,2:38:06.59,2:38:08.44,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不!
Dialogue: 0,2:38:08.49,2:38:11.23,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能从我身边夺走我的儿子!
Dialogue: 0,2:38:11.25,2:38:13.39,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不! 不!
Dialogue: 0,2:38:24.73,2:38:26.08,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,法拉米尔
Dialogue: 0,2:38:39.94,2:38:43.80,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,埃克瑟里昂之子德内索尔就这样死去了
Dialogue: 0,2:38:54.10,2:39:00.56,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪山林燃烧
Dialogue: 0,2:39:00.91,2:39:08.07,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪如红露降下
Dialogue: 0,2:39:08.12,2:39:18.23,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪落入佩兰诺原野
Dialogue: 0,2:39:11.35,2:39:13.76,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,把他们赶进河里!
Dialogue: 0,2:39:15.95,2:39:18.35,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,保卫城市!
Dialogue: 0,2:39:57.95,2:39:59.71,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,重新列队!
Dialogue: 0,2:40:00.99,2:40:02.80,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,重新列队!
Dialogue: 0,2:40:09.97,2:40:12.98,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,吹响冲锋号角! 迎头痛击!
Dialogue: 0,2:40:13.16,2:40:15.74,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,冲锋!
Dialogue: 0,2:41:34.31,2:41:35.77,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,把他砍倒!
Dialogue: 0,2:42:02.37,2:42:05.03,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,抓住缰绳, 向左拉!
Dialogue: 0,2:42:07.26,2:42:08.31,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,向左!
Dialogue: 0,2:42:26.08,2:42:27.81,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准它们的头!
Dialogue: 0,2:42:33.73,2:42:37.25,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,放倒它! 放倒它! 放倒它!
Dialogue: 0,2:42:50.87,2:42:52.23,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,梅利!
Dialogue: 0,2:44:05.75,2:44:07.89,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得结局不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,2:44:09.14,2:44:10.42,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,结局?
Dialogue: 0,2:44:11.88,2:44:14.39,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不, 这并不是旅程的终点
Dialogue: 0,2:44:16.47,2:44:19.30,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,死亡只不过是另一条
Dialogue: 0,2:44:20.11,2:44:22.24,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须要走的路
Dialogue: 0,2:44:23.07,2:44:26.71,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界的灰色雨帘卷起
Dialogue: 0,2:44:26.83,2:44:30.19,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都化做银色琉璃
Dialogue: 0,2:44:32.50,2:44:34.51,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,然后你就会看见了
Dialogue: 0,2:44:36.42,2:44:38.40,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,什么? 甘道夫
Dialogue: 0,2:44:39.93,2:44:41.41,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,看见什么?
Dialogue: 0,2:44:42.47,2:44:44.07,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,白色海岸
Dialogue: 0,2:44:46.43,2:44:48.41,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,和更远的彼方
Dialogue: 0,2:44:50.14,2:44:52.18,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,一片翠绿的乡野上
Dialogue: 0,2:44:52.85,2:44:55.09,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,是飞升的朝阳
Dialogue: 0,2:44:59.76,2:45:01.21,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,喔
Dialogue: 0,2:45:01.46,2:45:03.09,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,那也不算太坏
Dialogue: 0,2:45:03.17,2:45:04.40,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,2:45:06.66,2:45:08.26,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,确实不坏
Dialogue: 0,2:45:24.70,2:45:28.01,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,集合! 向我集合!
Dialogue: 0,2:45:48.89,2:45:52.95,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,享用他的血肉吧
Dialogue: 0,2:45:57.70,2:46:00.03,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你敢碰他我就杀了你
Dialogue: 0,2:46:00.03,2:46:05.35,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,别挡在纳芝古尔和他的猎物之间
Dialogue: 0,2:46:31.08,2:46:38.29,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪蠢货! 世上没有活着的男儿能杀死我!
Dialogue: 0,2:46:38.40,2:46:47.66,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪你会被带走, 超越一切黑暗
Dialogue: 0,2:46:47.79,2:46:55.47,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪肉体尽被吞噬, 你颤抖的意志
Dialogue: 0,2:46:55.56,2:47:01.61,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪赤裸于无睑之眼面前
Dialogue: 0,2:47:14.16,2:47:17.70,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这帮杂碎海盗, 又迟到了!
Dialogue: 0,2:47:17.72,2:47:20.03,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这里有些刀剑活儿要做
Dialogue: 0,2:47:20.05,2:47:21.89,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,快下来, 你们这帮海耗子!
Dialogue: 0,2:47:21.91,2:47:23.87,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,下船啊!
Dialogue: 0,2:47:38.60,2:47:41.16,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我俩都有很多要对付
Dialogue: 0,2:47:41.18,2:47:43.64,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,愿最强的矮人获胜
Dialogue: 0,2:48:01.01,2:48:03.07,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你这蠢货
Dialogue: 0,2:48:03.09,2:48:06.48,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,没有男人能杀死我
Dialogue: 0,2:48:08.84,2:48:12.02,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这就去死吧
Dialogue: 0,2:48:22.69,2:48:24.57,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是男人
Dialogue: 0,2:48:24.57,2:48:34.57,remark,,0000,0000,0000,,*瑞文戴尔的精灵格洛芬德尔曾预言"无人能杀死安格玛巫王",\N"人类"与"男人"在英文中是同一个单词, 此处是双关的用法
Dialogue: 0,2:48:41.23,2:48:42.96,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,十五! 十六!
Dialogue: 0,2:48:42.99,2:48:44.44,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,十七!
Dialogue: 0,2:48:52.55,2:48:54.08,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,梅利!
Dialogue: 0,2:49:36.54,2:49:37.99,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,莱戈拉斯!
Dialogue: 0,2:50:00.63,2:50:03.49,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,三十三, 三十四
Dialogue: 0,2:50:50.16,2:50:52.27,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,那还是只能算一个!
Dialogue: 0,2:50:52.35,2:50:54.36,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,快点啊, 快点!
Dialogue: 0,2:51:38.60,2:51:41.13,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我认得你的脸
Dialogue: 0,2:51:43.26,2:51:45.04,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,伊奥温
Dialogue: 0,2:51:47.73,2:51:49.74,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼睛看不清了
Dialogue: 0,2:51:51.19,2:51:52.70,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,2:51:53.38,2:51:54.86,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,2:51:56.21,2:52:04.04,rohan_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪超越死亡
Dialogue: 0,2:51:57.14,2:51:59.30,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我要救你
Dialogue: 0,2:52:00.85,2:52:03.24,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你已经做到了
Dialogue: 0,2:52:09.02,2:52:15.57,rohan_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪走出失落, 走出生命
Dialogue: 0,2:52:06.95,2:52:08.46,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,伊奥温...
Dialogue: 0,2:52:10.14,2:52:12.25,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我的身体已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,2:52:17.67,2:52:19.95,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你必须让我走
Dialogue: 0,2:52:24.08,2:52:38.66,rohan_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪走向长久的荣耀
Dialogue: 0,2:52:26.00,2:52:28.28,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去我的先祖那里
Dialogue: 0,2:52:30.01,2:52:32.32,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,在他们的伟业相伴之下
Dialogue: 0,2:52:33.27,2:52:35.98,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我应该不会感到羞愧
Dialogue: 0,2:52:53.27,2:52:54.63,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,伊奥温
Dialogue: 0,2:53:41.40,2:53:43.66,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,放了我们
Dialogue: 0,2:53:45.80,2:53:47.30,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,坏主意
Dialogue: 0,2:53:47.65,2:53:49.94,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这些家伙在遇上麻烦时很有用
Dialogue: 0,2:53:49.94,2:53:51.47,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,虽说他们已经死了
Dialogue: 0,2:53:51.49,2:53:54.15,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你向我们保证过
Dialogue: 0,2:53:55.41,2:53:57.84,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你们的誓言已得践行
Dialogue: 0,2:53:58.84,2:54:00.07,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,2:54:01.05,2:54:02.58,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,愿你们安息
Dialogue: 0,2:54:46.12,2:54:47.63,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,梅利
Dialogue: 0,2:54:48.83,2:54:52.62,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不!
Dialogue: 0,2:54:55.48,2:54:58.59,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不!
Dialogue: 0,2:55:00.70,2:55:05.09,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪你我之间阴影深重
Dialogue: 0,2:55:05.24,2:55:09.33,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪你曾来过, 亦将远离我们
Dialogue: 0,2:55:09.38,2:55:13.77,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪万物皆荣枯有数
Dialogue: 0,2:55:14.08,2:55:21.68,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪众生终尽归荒芜
Dialogue: 0,2:55:21.90,2:55:25.69,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}♪叹息着
Dialogue: 0,2:55:25.79,2:55:29.76,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}♪你转过身去
Dialogue: 0,2:55:29.81,2:55:34.03,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}♪心中沉重
Dialogue: 0,2:55:34.08,2:55:38.89,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}♪无法言语
Dialogue: 0,2:55:38.92,2:55:42.41,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}♪你看
Dialogue: 0,2:55:42.48,2:55:46.77,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}♪世界已然更替
Dialogue: 0,2:55:46.82,2:55:51.14,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}♪一去不回
Dialogue: 0,2:56:15.73,2:56:24.30,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}♪看青翠树叶渐次由黄而陨
Dialogue: 0,2:56:27.32,2:56:32.34,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}♪看阳光缓缓消逝
Dialogue: 0,2:56:32.37,2:56:39.39,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}♪我只愿将你
Dialogue: 0,2:56:39.42,2:56:43.46,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}♪紧拥怀里
Dialogue: 0,2:56:45.19,2:56:46.65,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,梅利!
Dialogue: 0,2:56:48.08,2:56:49.73,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,梅利!
Dialogue: 0,2:57:01.63,2:57:03.03,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,梅利
Dialogue: 0,2:57:05.69,2:57:07.30,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,梅利, 是我
Dialogue: 0,2:57:09.63,2:57:11.21,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,是皮平
Dialogue: 0,2:57:13.62,2:57:15.96,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你会找到我的
Dialogue: 0,2:57:16.13,2:57:17.54,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,2:57:19.62,2:57:21.53,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你会抛下我吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:57:22.46,2:57:24.16,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不, 梅利
Dialogue: 0,2:57:25.44,2:57:27.37,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我会照顾你
Dialogue: 0,2:58:11.39,2:58:13.14,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,把手拿开!
Dialogue: 0,2:58:13.22,2:58:16.68,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,那件亮闪闪的衣服是我的
Dialogue: 0,2:58:16.71,2:58:21.12,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这个要和其它所有东西一起交给巨眼
Dialogue: 0,2:58:22.38,2:58:26.17,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不听莫古尔臭耗子下的命令!
Dialogue: 0,2:58:22.38,2:58:32.38,remark,,0000,0000,0000,,*莫古尔是辛达语, 意为"巫术"或"邪术", 这里指的\N是米纳斯莫古尔, 即被戒灵占据的巫术之塔
Dialogue: 0,2:58:27.07,2:58:29.10,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你要敢碰
Dialogue: 0,2:58:29.10,2:58:32.64,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我就把这刀子戳进你肠子里
Dialogue: 0,2:58:52.79,2:58:54.88,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,那个杂碎还想一刀砍了我
Dialogue: 0,2:58:54.90,2:58:56.23,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,杀了他!
Dialogue: 0,3:00:39.79,3:00:41.50,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这一下是为弗罗多!
Dialogue: 0,3:00:42.18,3:00:43.98,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这是为夏尔!
Dialogue: 0,3:00:47.70,3:00:50.36,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这下是为了我家老爹!
Dialogue: 0,3:01:19.57,3:01:22.88,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你这脏耗子别吱吱乱叫
Dialogue: 0,3:01:23.93,3:01:28.47,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我要给你这只该戳的猪放点血
Dialogue: 0,3:01:36.08,3:01:37.88,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,让我先给你放点血再说
Dialogue: 0,3:01:37.93,3:01:39.04,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,山姆!
Dialogue: 0,3:01:44.53,3:01:46.62,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 山姆, 我很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,3:01:46.67,3:01:48.32,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我对一切都很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,3:01:48.90,3:01:50.11,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我带你离开这里
Dialogue: 0,3:01:50.11,3:01:53.02,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,太迟了, 已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,3:01:53.04,3:01:54.95,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他们把它拿走了
Dialogue: 0,3:01:55.17,3:01:56.38,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,山姆
Dialogue: 0,3:01:56.83,3:01:58.69,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他们拿走了魔戒
Dialogue: 0,3:01:59.06,3:02:01.35,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思, 可他们没拿
Dialogue: 0,3:02:13.72,3:02:15.98,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为你死了
Dialogue: 0,3:02:16.33,3:02:18.11,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就拿了
Dialogue: 0,3:02:19.14,3:02:21.00,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,只是帮你收着
Dialogue: 0,3:02:22.48,3:02:24.23,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,把它给我
Dialogue: 0,3:02:27.82,3:02:29.75,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,把魔戒给我, 山姆
Dialogue: 0,3:02:34.87,3:02:36.05,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,山姆
Dialogue: 0,3:02:37.56,3:02:39.62,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,把魔戒给我
Dialogue: 0,3:03:00.27,3:03:02.02,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你必须明白
Dialogue: 0,3:03:05.04,3:03:06.94,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,魔戒是我的重担
Dialogue: 0,3:03:07.97,3:03:10.03,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,它会毁了你的, 山姆
Dialogue: 0,3:03:13.39,3:03:15.15,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,它会毁了你的, 山姆
Dialogue: 0,3:03:16.63,3:03:18.44,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,最好给你找些衣服来
Dialogue: 0,3:03:18.49,3:03:21.62,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能在魔多光着身子走路
Dialogue: 0,3:03:43.20,3:03:45.01,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们办到了, 弗罗多先生
Dialogue: 0,3:03:46.04,3:03:47.97,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们走到魔多了
Dialogue: 0,3:03:49.58,3:03:51.51,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他们人太多了
Dialogue: 0,3:03:52.19,3:03:54.72,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们没法不被发现地穿过去
Dialogue: 0,3:03:59.92,3:04:02.93,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,是他, 是巨眼
Dialogue: 0,3:04:11.01,3:04:13.39,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须进去, 弗罗多先生
Dialogue: 0,3:04:14.14,3:04:16.08,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,没别的办法
Dialogue: 0,3:04:19.04,3:04:20.57,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,3:04:20.72,3:04:23.38,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,还是先把走下山当做第一步吧
Dialogue: 0,3:04:32.84,3:04:35.75,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经看不到弗罗多的行踪了
Dialogue: 0,3:04:37.46,3:04:39.99,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗愈发浓重
Dialogue: 0,3:04:40.37,3:04:42.60,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,如果索隆得到了魔戒, 我们会知道的
Dialogue: 0,3:04:42.62,3:04:44.96,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,那只是时间问题
Dialogue: 0,3:04:46.66,3:04:49.22,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他确实吃了一场败仗, 但是...
Dialogue: 0,3:04:50.03,3:04:54.42,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,在魔多的高墙背后, 敌人正在重整军队
Dialogue: 0,3:04:54.59,3:04:56.45,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,让他呆在那里
Dialogue: 0,3:04:56.50,3:04:59.44,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,让他烂在那里! 我们为什么要管?
Dialogue: 0,3:04:59.46,3:05:04.56,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,因为现在挡在弗罗多和厄运山之间的有一万个兽人
Dialogue: 0,3:05:11.48,3:05:13.64,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我这是让他去送死
Dialogue: 0,3:05:15.50,3:05:16.88,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,3:05:17.30,3:05:19.34,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,弗罗多仍然有希望
Dialogue: 0,3:05:20.04,3:05:24.58,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他需要时间, 需要穿越高戈罗斯平原的安全通路
Dialogue: 0,3:05:20.04,3:05:28.12,remark,,0000,0000,0000,,*高戈罗斯意为"恐怖之地", 是魔多西北面一片荒废的平原,\N索隆的大军就屯兵于此
Dialogue: 0,3:05:25.28,3:05:26.89,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们能为他提供这些
Dialogue: 0,3:05:26.94,3:05:28.12,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么提供?
Dialogue: 0,3:05:28.17,3:05:30.90,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,引出索隆的军队
Dialogue: 0,3:05:31.06,3:05:32.86,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,让他的地盘空无一人
Dialogue: 0,3:05:33.44,3:05:36.55,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,然后我们集结所有兵力进军黑门
Dialogue: 0,3:05:37.08,3:05:40.24,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能通过武力获胜
Dialogue: 0,3:05:40.26,3:05:42.02,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不能为我们自己赢得胜利
Dialogue: 0,3:05:42.05,3:05:47.37,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,但若能让索隆之眼牢牢注视我们, 就能给弗罗多一个机会
Dialogue: 0,3:05:49.37,3:05:53.06,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,让索隆对其他的动作毫无察觉
Dialogue: 0,3:05:53.94,3:05:55.12,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,一次声东击西
Dialogue: 0,3:05:55.15,3:05:57.20,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,注定会有伤亡
Dialogue: 0,3:05:57.23,3:05:59.91,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,赢面很小
Dialogue: 0,3:06:01.04,3:06:03.08,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们还等什么?
Dialogue: 0,3:06:03.25,3:06:05.38,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,索隆会怀疑这是个陷阱
Dialogue: 0,3:06:06.51,3:06:08.50,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他不会上钩的
Dialogue: 0,3:06:09.98,3:06:12.08,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 我认为他会的
Dialogue: 0,3:06:46.71,3:06:49.37,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你追捕我很久了
Dialogue: 0,3:06:49.72,3:06:52.06,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,而我也躲避了很久
Dialogue: 0,3:06:53.34,3:06:54.82,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,3:06:56.65,3:06:59.31,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,看这伊伦迪尔之剑
Dialogue: 0,3:07:43.58,3:07:46.01,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这座城市已陷入沉寂
Dialogue: 0,3:07:47.79,3:07:50.58,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,阳光下已不再温暖
Dialogue: 0,3:07:51.56,3:07:53.64,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,如此寒冷刺骨
Dialogue: 0,3:07:56.45,3:07:59.11,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这只是第一场春雨带来的湿气
Dialogue: 0,3:08:05.73,3:08:08.64,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信这黑暗不会持续下去
Dialogue: 0,3:08:37.55,3:08:39.56,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,看, 那些兽人
Dialogue: 0,3:08:39.58,3:08:41.57,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,它们走了
Dialogue: 0,3:08:42.82,3:08:44.95,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你瞧, 弗罗多先生
Dialogue: 0,3:08:45.03,3:08:47.01,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,终于交上好运了
Dialogue: 0,3:08:47.34,3:08:49.22,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,快走, 你这懒虫!
Dialogue: 0,3:08:50.45,3:08:53.41,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,走啊! 快点!
Dialogue: 0,3:09:01.77,3:09:04.53,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,走啊, 你们这些杂碎
Dialogue: 0,3:09:05.16,3:09:08.54,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我要抽到你们皮开肉绽
Dialogue: 0,3:09:12.46,3:09:14.29,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,快走!
Dialogue: 0,3:09:14.49,3:09:16.60,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才跟你们说什么了?!
Dialogue: 0,3:09:23.52,3:09:25.21,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,起来!
Dialogue: 0,3:09:25.51,3:09:27.99,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,走路, 你们这些懒虫!
Dialogue: 0,3:09:28.09,3:09:32.43,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个直接去最前排!
Dialogue: 0,3:09:32.48,3:09:34.97,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,快走! 继续走! 集合!
Dialogue: 0,3:09:35.02,3:09:37.88,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,快走! 快走! 快走!
Dialogue: 0,3:09:49.72,3:09:51.78,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,去大门那里, 懒虫们!
Dialogue: 0,3:09:51.78,3:09:53.51,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,现在去, 快点走!
Dialogue: 0,3:10:03.17,3:10:06.71,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你们都不知道这是在打仗吗?
Dialogue: 0,3:10:28.82,3:10:31.95,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,队伍立定!
Dialogue: 0,3:10:35.94,3:10:39.28,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,检查!
Dialogue: 0,3:10:39.43,3:10:41.72,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,山姆, 帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,3:10:41.79,3:10:43.50,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,弗罗多先生!
Dialogue: 0,3:10:46.48,3:10:48.94,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,站起来, 弗罗多先生, 站起来!
Dialogue: 0,3:10:48.97,3:10:50.83,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,它太重了
Dialogue: 0,3:11:00.03,3:11:01.52,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 不
Dialogue: 0,3:11:06.73,3:11:09.34,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么办? 我们怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,3:11:11.90,3:11:13.28,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,-打我  -什么?
Dialogue: 0,3:11:13.31,3:11:15.47,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,山姆, 打我, 打起架来
Dialogue: 0,3:11:15.52,3:11:16.87,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,离我远点!
Dialogue: 0,3:11:17.50,3:11:19.96,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,没人可以推我, 你这臭蛆虫
Dialogue: 0,3:11:28.82,3:11:30.45,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,离我远点!
Dialogue: 0,3:11:31.55,3:11:34.06,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,揍他! 揍他!
Dialogue: 0,3:11:36.35,3:11:40.96,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,喂! 敢继续闹事我就把你们肠子捅出来!
Dialogue: 0,3:11:40.99,3:11:43.15,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,走, 山姆, 就现在!
Dialogue: 0,3:11:52.33,3:11:53.96,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,继续走, 杂碎!
Dialogue: 0,3:11:53.99,3:11:56.14,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,滚回去列队!
Dialogue: 0,3:11:56.55,3:11:58.28,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些蛆虫!
Dialogue: 0,3:11:58.95,3:12:01.74,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,站回队里去, 你们这些懒虫!
Dialogue: 0,3:12:04.10,3:12:07.49,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,挖呀, 懒虫, 快走
Dialogue: 0,3:12:10.35,3:12:11.73,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,快走!
Dialogue: 0,3:12:56.27,3:12:57.98,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能...
Dialogue: 0,3:12:58.65,3:13:01.69,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能...不能控制魔戒了, 山姆
Dialogue: 0,3:13:02.49,3:13:04.05,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,它...它...
Dialogue: 0,3:13:04.10,3:13:06.58,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,它太重了, 扛不动
Dialogue: 0,3:13:07.51,3:13:09.94,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,它...真的太重了
Dialogue: 0,3:13:15.49,3:13:18.81,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们朝那边走, 尽量直走
Dialogue: 0,3:13:19.20,3:13:22.52,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不是必须的东西都没必要带了
Dialogue: 0,3:13:37.77,3:13:39.28,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,弗罗多先生
Dialogue: 0,3:13:41.06,3:13:42.54,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,3:13:45.23,3:13:47.03,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,那上面有光
Dialogue: 0,3:13:47.41,3:13:49.04,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,有美丽的东西
Dialogue: 0,3:13:49.49,3:13:51.95,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,是阴影碰不到的
Dialogue: 0,3:14:42.72,3:14:44.57,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,喝我的吧
Dialogue: 0,3:14:44.97,3:14:46.86,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,还剩下最后几滴
Dialogue: 0,3:15:02.01,3:15:05.00,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,回去的路上就没有剩的了
Dialogue: 0,3:15:05.73,3:15:09.22,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得不会有回去的路了, 弗罗多先生
Dialogue: 0,3:16:01.79,3:16:04.17,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,弗罗多, 趴下!
Dialogue: 0,3:16:05.75,3:16:07.63,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,躲起来!
Dialogue: 0,3:16:17.57,3:16:19.53,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,弗罗多!
Dialogue: 0,3:16:25.60,3:16:27.36,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在哪儿?
Dialogue: 0,3:17:03.22,3:17:06.50,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,让黑地的主人出来!
Dialogue: 0,3:17:07.13,3:17:09.84,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,让他接受正义的审判!
Dialogue: 0,3:17:52.00,3:18:01.00,remark,,0000,0000,0000,,*这里迎战的来者是索隆之口. 原著中\N他是投靠索隆的黑努美诺尔人,并非戒灵或兽人
Dialogue: 0,3:17:53.38,3:17:58.05,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我的主人, 伟大的索隆, 欢迎你们到来
Dialogue: 0,3:18:03.27,3:18:07.28,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这群乌合之众里可有个头领来与我商谈?
Dialogue: 0,3:18:07.33,3:18:10.59,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们并不是来跟索隆商谈的
Dialogue: 0,3:18:10.64,3:18:13.10,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他言而无信, 天怒人怨
Dialogue: 0,3:18:13.23,3:18:14.91,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,就告诉你的主子
Dialogue: 0,3:18:14.93,3:18:17.24,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,魔多的大军必须解散
Dialogue: 0,3:18:17.27,3:18:20.05,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他必须离开此地, 永不回返
Dialogue: 0,3:18:20.98,3:18:23.92,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,灰胡子老头
Dialogue: 0,3:18:24.95,3:18:29.21,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,有个信物, 他让我拿给你看
Dialogue: 0,3:18:34.51,3:18:35.76,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,弗罗多
Dialogue: 0,3:18:38.62,3:18:39.90,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,弗罗多
Dialogue: 0,3:18:40.66,3:18:41.66,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,安静
Dialogue: 0,3:18:41.66,3:18:42.71,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不!
Dialogue: 0,3:18:42.76,3:18:44.04,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,安静!
Dialogue: 0,3:18:45.95,3:18:49.66,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,看来那个半身人和你很亲近
Dialogue: 0,3:18:50.74,3:18:55.08,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,要知道他正在主人的款待下受着痛苦折磨
Dialogue: 0,3:19:00.30,3:19:03.09,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,谁会想到这么一个小东西
Dialogue: 0,3:19:03.09,3:19:06.53,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,竟能忍受这么多的痛苦?
Dialogue: 0,3:19:08.74,3:19:11.14,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他可受苦了, 甘道夫
Dialogue: 0,3:19:11.32,3:19:13.03,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他可受苦了
Dialogue: 0,3:19:19.78,3:19:21.38,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这是谁啊?
Dialogue: 0,3:19:21.41,3:19:23.74,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,伊西尔德的后裔?
Dialogue: 0,3:19:23.77,3:19:27.10,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,想要为王, 只有一把破碎的精灵剑可不行
Dialogue: 0,3:19:31.70,3:19:34.53,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我猜这就没什么好谈的了
Dialogue: 0,3:19:36.36,3:19:38.12,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会相信
Dialogue: 0,3:19:39.15,3:19:41.08,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不会相信
Dialogue: 0,3:19:57.04,3:19:58.85,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,后撤
Dialogue: 0,3:19:59.20,3:20:00.80,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,后撤!
Dialogue: 0,3:20:13.40,3:20:15.26,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,它移开了, 弗罗多先生
Dialogue: 0,3:20:17.47,3:20:20.70,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,火光继续朝前去了, 向北边走了
Dialogue: 0,3:20:20.98,3:20:23.04,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么东西吸引了他的目光
Dialogue: 0,3:20:40.43,3:20:43.64,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,坚守阵线! 坚守阵线
Dialogue: 0,3:20:45.02,3:20:47.86,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,冈多之子, 罗翰之子
Dialogue: 0,3:20:47.88,3:20:49.96,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我的弟兄们!
Dialogue: 0,3:20:52.15,3:20:54.20,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我从你们眼里看出
Dialogue: 0,3:20:54.35,3:20:57.84,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,同样攫在我心头的恐惧
Dialogue: 0,3:21:00.40,3:21:04.14,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,或许有一天, 人类的勇气衰竭
Dialogue: 0,3:21:04.17,3:21:07.86,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们抛弃朋友, 断绝一切友谊的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,3:21:07.91,3:21:10.21,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,但绝不是今天
Dialogue: 0,3:21:10.89,3:21:14.15,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,那时饿狼群集, 盾牌碎裂
Dialogue: 0,3:21:14.18,3:21:17.34,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,人类纪元分崩离析
Dialogue: 0,3:21:17.37,3:21:19.83,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,但绝不是今天
Dialogue: 0,3:21:19.85,3:21:21.91,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,今天, 我们奋力一战!
Dialogue: 0,3:21:23.51,3:21:27.70,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我以这沃土上你们珍视的一切
Dialogue: 0,3:21:27.73,3:21:32.07,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,请你们站出身来, 西方之民!
Dialogue: 0,3:23:00.48,3:23:04.19,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,从没想过我会跟精灵并肩战死
Dialogue: 0,3:23:04.52,3:23:07.35,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,跟朋友并肩战死怎样?
Dialogue: 0,3:23:10.41,3:23:11.82,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,成啊
Dialogue: 0,3:23:13.02,3:23:14.85,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,这我做得到
Dialogue: 0,3:23:19.71,3:23:27.85,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪那就让死亡终结它
Dialogue: 0,3:23:28.04,3:23:36.57,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪他占据我心中最后的领地
Dialogue: 0,3:23:45.09,3:23:47.38,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得夏尔吗, 弗罗多先生?
Dialogue: 0,3:23:49.61,3:23:58.00,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪那就让死亡终结它
Dialogue: 0,3:23:50.16,3:23:52.12,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,很快就是春天了
Dialogue: 0,3:23:53.25,3:23:55.31,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,花园里会开满鲜花
Dialogue: 0,3:23:56.16,3:23:59.35,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,鸟儿会在榛树丛里搭窝
Dialogue: 0,3:24:01.10,3:24:04.87,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,他们会在低田里种下夏麦
Dialogue: 0,3:24:05.05,3:24:14.47,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪他占据我心中最后的领地
Dialogue: 0,3:24:06.15,3:24:10.29,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,伴着奶油吃掉新采的草莓
Dialogue: 0,3:24:12.42,3:24:15.21,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得草莓的味道吗?
Dialogue: 0,3:24:16.66,3:24:18.44,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不, 山姆
Dialogue: 0,3:24:18.49,3:24:20.83,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我记不起食物的滋味
Dialogue: 0,3:24:22.51,3:24:25.85,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,记不起水流的声音
Dialogue: 0,3:24:25.97,3:24:29.13,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,也记不起草叶的触感
Dialogue: 0,3:24:30.51,3:24:32.04,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在
Dialogue: 0,3:24:32.92,3:24:34.95,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,在黑暗里赤身裸体
Dialogue: 0,3:24:36.01,3:24:38.39,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,什么...什么也没有
Dialogue: 0,3:24:38.42,3:24:43.01,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我和那火焰之轮当中无遮无拦
Dialogue: 0,3:24:44.44,3:24:46.22,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我能看见他
Dialogue: 0,3:24:46.77,3:24:48.98,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,睁着眼睛就能看见
Dialogue: 0,3:24:49.48,3:24:51.87,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,那就让我们解决掉它吧
Dialogue: 0,3:24:52.57,3:24:54.60,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,一了百了
Dialogue: 0,3:24:55.36,3:24:57.11,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧, 弗罗多先生
Dialogue: 0,3:24:57.22,3:25:03.29,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪到尽头
Dialogue: 0,3:24:57.66,3:25:00.07,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能替你拿戒指
Dialogue: 0,3:25:00.80,3:25:02.88,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,但我可以背着你走
Dialogue: 0,3:25:03.34,3:25:04.51,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,走啊!
Dialogue: 0,3:25:03.50,3:25:23.45,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪我会随他直到尽头
Dialogue: 0,3:25:35.66,3:25:38.54,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,阿拉贡
Dialogue: 0,3:25:49.98,3:25:53.25,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,埃勒萨
