Dialogue: 0,3:26:42.00,3:26:43.81,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,看, 弗罗多先生
Dialogue: 0,3:26:44.21,3:26:45.82,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,有条门廊
Dialogue: 0,3:26:47.22,3:26:55.01,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪我已给你承诺
Dialogue: 0,3:26:47.00,3:26:48.85,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就快到了
Dialogue: 0,3:26:50.96,3:26:55.20,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,聪明的霍比特人爬得好高啊!
Dialogue: 0,3:26:55.65,3:27:12.89,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪绝不打破
Dialogue: 0,3:27:09.00,3:27:11.51,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不能走那条路
Dialogue: 0,3:27:12.04,3:27:14.48,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不能伤到宝贝
Dialogue: 0,3:27:14.50,3:27:16.48,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你发过誓的!
Dialogue: 0,3:27:16.56,3:27:18.92,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你对宝贝发过誓!
Dialogue: 0,3:27:14.32,3:27:25.14,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪绝不逃避
Dialogue: 0,3:27:20.25,3:27:22.18,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,斯米戈尔保证过!
Dialogue: 0,3:27:23.48,3:27:25.24,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,斯米戈尔撒谎了
Dialogue: 0,3:27:42.53,3:27:49.66,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪让魔多知晓
