Dialogue: 0,3:29:45.84,3:29:48.30,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,把它扔进火里!
Dialogue: 0,3:30:01.88,3:30:04.13,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,你还在等什么?
Dialogue: 0,3:30:06.37,3:30:08.88,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,扔掉就好了!
Dialogue: 0,3:30:41.93,3:30:44.01,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,魔戒是我的
