Dialogue: 0,3:33:05.59,3:33:21.12,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪唯此一途, 方可毁其邪恶
Dialogue: 0,3:33:51.66,3:33:53.26,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,把手给我!
Dialogue: 0,3:34:02.00,3:34:03.85,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,抓住我的手!
Dialogue: 0,3:34:06.87,3:34:08.02,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不!
Dialogue: 0,3:34:08.02,3:34:15.65,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪他占据我心中最后的领地
Dialogue: 0,3:34:15.65,3:34:17.56,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,不许放手
Dialogue: 0,3:34:17.56,3:34:29.48,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪我会随他直到尽头
Dialogue: 0,3:34:22.20,3:34:23.68,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,别放手
Dialogue: 0,3:34:25.33,3:34:27.12,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,抓上来!
