Dialogue: 0,3:36:26.76,3:36:36.30,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪烈焰山峰释出毁灭之全力
Dialogue: 0,3:37:23.70,3:37:25.51,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,毁掉它了
Dialogue: 0,3:37:30.15,3:37:31.86,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,3:37:32.41,3:37:34.29,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊, 弗罗多先生
Dialogue: 0,3:37:35.87,3:37:37.88,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,都结束了
Dialogue: 0,3:38:03.68,3:38:05.81,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我能看到夏尔了
Dialogue: 0,3:38:08.42,3:38:10.60,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,白兰地河
Dialogue: 0,3:38:12.94,3:38:14.89,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,袋底洞
Dialogue: 0,3:38:17.28,3:38:19.64,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,甘道夫的焰火
Dialogue: 0,3:38:20.54,3:38:24.23,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,宴会树上的灯火
Dialogue: 0,3:38:25.61,3:38:28.54,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,罗茜·科顿在跳舞
Dialogue: 0,3:38:29.87,3:38:32.46,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,她的头发上系着缎带
Dialogue: 0,3:38:35.52,3:38:38.18,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我要是会和什么人结婚的话
Dialogue: 0,3:38:39.58,3:38:41.87,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定就是她了
Dialogue: 0,3:38:42.97,3:38:45.13,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定就是她了
Dialogue: 0,3:38:57.00,3:39:00.36,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我很高兴能跟你一起, 山姆怀斯·甘姆齐
Dialogue: 0,3:39:04.95,3:39:07.69,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,在这一切结束的时候
Dialogue: 0,3:39:29.45,3:39:39.08,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪梦中我被轻轻托起
Dialogue: 0,3:39:39.26,3:39:44.28,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪穿过深沉的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,3:39:44.85,3:39:51.65,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪越过火焰的河流
Dialogue: 0,3:39:51.65,3:40:00.19,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪乘着风一般轻柔的羽翼
Dialogue: 0,3:40:00.31,3:40:07.74,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪世上发生了什么?
Dialogue: 0,3:40:07.76,3:40:24.18,sindarin_ost,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\move(100, 50, 120, 50)}♪一切悲伤是否都将消逝?
Dialogue: 0,3:40:57.45,3:40:59.33,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,甘道夫?
Dialogue: 0,3:41:19.21,3:41:20.69,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,弗罗多!
Dialogue: 0,3:41:40.99,3:41:42.52,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,吉穆利!
Dialogue: 0,3:43:25.68,3:43:28.94,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,王者的时代自此而始
Dialogue: 0,3:43:34.44,3:43:36.87,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,愿他们得到庇佑
Dialogue: 0,3:43:57.02,3:44:01.19,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,今天并不仅属于一人, 而是属于人类全体
Dialogue: 0,3:44:03.39,3:44:06.28,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,让我们一起重建这个世界
Dialogue: 0,3:44:06.48,3:44:09.94,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,我们便可在和平的日子里共同分享
Dialogue: 0,3:44:23.09,3:44:27.46,main_body,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fad(500,500)\fn楷体}♪远离海域{\b0}
